cards = [{"rawname":"2D Kal","imagePath":"2D_Kal.jpg","name":"2D Kal","form":"2D Form","number":0,"rarity":"4","caption":"I shall pour down a shower of light upon my master!","defense":"7000","lore":"The soul of a kaleidoscope owned by a witch. It's terrific fun to get lost in the world of illusions she summons up, where the show of dancing sparkling color never ends.","attack":"3500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"2D Kal","imagePath":"3D_Kal.jpg","name":"3D Kal","form":"3D Form","number":1,"rarity":"5","caption":"The moment where reminiscence meets incandescence... That's my gift to you, master!","defense":"13800","lore":"The soul of a kaleidoscope owned by a witch. Possessing the power to change all that lies within the kaleidoscope, she'll whisk you away to an illusory world where nothing is still and everything glimmers!","attack":"11500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Aboro","imagePath":"Aboro.jpg","name":"Aboro","form":"Original Form","number":2,"rarity":"1","caption":"U-Uh oh... Now, what were those ninja skills I learned again? I'm sure there was one called...ESCAPE!","defense":"1400","lore":"The soul of a female ninja. She has absolutely no control over where her throwing knives end up, and is constantly angering her fellow ninja Kaede with her break-and-run tactics.","attack":"1310","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Achilles","imagePath":"Achilles.jpg","name":"Achilles","form":"Original Form","number":3,"rarity":"4","caption":"Charge forth! Victory will surely be ours!","defense":"8900","lore":"A famous hero from Greek mythology, and the protagonist of Homer's epic poem, The Iliad. A general in command of a huge army, Achilles stood on the front lines and battled alongside his soldiers. It's said that any who saw his hulky, muscular figure was like putty in his hands.","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Yoshitsune","imagePath":"Adult_Yoshitsune.jpg","name":"Adult Yoshitsune","form":"Young Form","number":4,"rarity":"5","caption":"Together, my brother and I will avenge our father!","defense":"13500","lore":"A heroic shogun from the Heian period. He was known during his childhood by the name Ushiwakamaru. He was separated from his mother, the legendarily beautiful Lady Tokiwa, at an early age, and entrusted to Kurama temple in Kyoto.","attack":"13500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Aegis","imagePath":"Aegis.jpg","name":"Aegis","form":"Original Form","number":5,"rarity":"5","caption":"Your pathetic attacks are as but a child's before my mighty shield","defense":"12750","lore":"The soul of a shield that once belonged to the Goddess Athena from Greek Mythology. She has a soft spot for Behemoths, and tries to protect it from evil. Now charged with your protection, she will never leave your side.","attack":"8800","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Agatha","imagePath":"Agatha.jpg","name":"Agatha","form":"Original Form","number":6,"rarity":"3","caption":"This is Agatha, awaiting orders!","defense":"4600","lore":"The soul of a helicopter that is used by the US Army. Agatha is known as the 'flying tank' on account of her heavy weaponry.","attack":"4900","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Agatha","imagePath":"Agatha_Mk._2.jpg","name":"Agatha Mk. 2","form":"Ultimate Form","number":7,"rarity":"4","caption":"Spotted! I've got eyeball on a drive-through, three o'clock!","defense":"7800","lore":"The soul of a helicopter that is used by the US Army. Agatha is known as the 'flying tank' on account of her heavy weaponry. She is fond of hamburgers, and has been seen hovering into many a drive-through.","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Agni","imagePath":"Agni.jpg","name":"Agni","form":"Original Form","number":8,"rarity":"4","caption":"Bathe in the flames of purgatory!","defense":"8500","lore":"A fire specialist, he is engulfed in fire, and his weapons and armor are imbued with the power of flames. Agni is a magic warrior. He is capable of both physical and magical attacks. Many find him to be a handy friend to have.","attack":"9500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Akaname","imagePath":"Akaname.jpg","name":"Akaname","form":"Original Form","number":9,"rarity":"4","caption":"Mmm. So many choices!","defense":"10080","lore":"A monstrous being of legend that likes to lick things. With so many surfaces to lick, hot springs are her favorite place to be in the whole wide world. Whenever she has a chance, she likes to lick candies, too. She especially loves red ones and strawberry is her favorite flavor. Kind of cute, don't you think? ","attack":"7890","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Alice","imagePath":"Alice.jpg","name":"Alice","form":"Original Form","number":10,"rarity":"5","caption":"I love going on adventures! And ones full of wonder at that!","defense":"12290","lore":"When this lady was a child, she went to a mysterious land and had the adventure of a lifetime. She has a soft and gentle manner, and looks younger than she actually is. Some say she's managed to stay young at heart by forgetting about all the things that happend to her in the past... She feels a mysterious sense of mission: she's not sure where it comes from, but she goes along with it anyway!","attack":"11080","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Alice","imagePath":"Alice_Hawk.jpg","name":"Alice [Hawk]","form":"Classic Form","number":11,"rarity":"5","caption":"I'm hungry for more adventures! Take me back to Wonderland!","defense":"15400","lore":"A revitalized Alice, back in touch with everything that made her beloved to millions. No one looks better in blue dress and pinafore! Back in business with all her old memories, she seems wiser than before, and her features have a slightly more adult air about them.","attack":"12600","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Alice","imagePath":"Alice_Shichi-Go-San.jpg","name":"Alice [Shichi-Go-San]","form":"Shichi-Go-San Form","number":12,"rarity":"5","caption":"Gah! I can barely move in these clothes!","defense":"12500","lore":"It turns out there's a children's festival back in Alice's home of Wonderland that's very reminiscent of the Japanese Shichi-Go-San festival. It's a place where anything can happen, after all. But if you look closely, you'll notice subtle differences between it and its Japanese counterpart. For instance, that thing that looks like a shrine? Well, it isn't a shrine. Is any of this real, or is it all part of Alice's dream? Well, that's another story...","attack":"15100","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Alice","imagePath":"Alice%2527s_Dress.jpg","name":"Alice's Dress","form":"Hawk Form","number":13,"rarity":"5","caption":"Oh! An Adventure in the sky? How curious!","defense":"13100","lore":"In Japan, dreaming of a hawk on New Year's Eve is considered lucky. In Alice's dream, she became a soaring hawk and flew around the world on a journey filled with adventure. She thought she would enjoy flying, but she reports that the sense of floating unfettered by gravity actually made her feel nauseous. It seems Alice could have an exciting adventure just about anywhere...","attack":"14200","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Alnasl","imagePath":"Alnasl.jpg","name":"Alnasl","form":"Original Form","number":14,"rarity":"3","caption":"All right! Here I go!","defense":"4300","lore":"A warrior known as \"the tip of the arrow.\" Flying like an arrow straight and true, she is the first to enter the enemy camp on her path of destruction. Her movements are too fast for even the gods to detect, and she can cut down her targets before they are aware of what is happening to them.","attack":"6400","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Altair","imagePath":"Altair.jpg","name":"Altair","form":"Original Form","number":15,"rarity":"4","caption":"Someday...I will go back to that time...","defense":"8350","lore":"Of noble descent, he lost everything due to the cunning trickery of his foes during a struggle for galactic supremacy. He entered the seedy underworld, and what do you know? He discovered he had a previously unknown talent for grievous butchery. He bides his time and watches vigilantly for a chance at revenge.","attack":"8350","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Amanojaku","imagePath":"Amanojaku.jpg","name":"Amanojaku","form":"Original Form","number":16,"rarity":"3","caption":"I don't actually like being around you, you know...","defense":"4050","lore":"A daemon in Japanese folklore. She loves nothing more than doing the exact opposite of what you want her to do.","attack":"3263","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Amanojaku","imagePath":"Amanojaku_HW.jpg","name":"Amanojaku [HW]","form":"Halloween Form","number":17,"rarity":"3","caption":"Hey! Quit staring! You're making me uncomfortable!","defense":"6200","lore":"A daemon in Japanese folklore. She dressed to impress, but she can still be a little spiky when folks stare at her.","attack":"3750","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Amaterasu","imagePath":"Amaterasu.jpg","name":"Amaterasu","form":"Original Form","number":18,"rarity":"5","caption":"I am life itself...","defense":"10040","lore":"The sun goddess who is the greatest of all the Japanese deities. She once hid herself inside a cave, thereby depriving the entire world of light.","attack":"12010","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Amaterasu","imagePath":"Amaterasu_In_Hiding.jpg","name":"Amaterasu [In Hiding]","form":"In Hiding Form","number":19,"rarity":"5","caption":"I'm never leaving this warm and comfy cave!","defense":"13800","lore":"The sun goddess, and the greatest of all Japanese deities. After falling for Nataraja's lie, she shut herself up inside Amano-Iwato cave, threatening the world once more with the prospect of everlasting darkness. Isn't it about time someone imposed a Japan-wide ban on sun goddesses stepping into dark and ominous caves? ","attack":"13800","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Amaymon","imagePath":"Amaymon.jpg","name":"Amaymon","form":"Original Form","number":20,"rarity":"4","caption":"Shall I tell you about my Bethie Baby? It won't take more than an hour...","defense":"8100","lore":"One of the eight princes of the underworld, responsible for the evil that is greed. He commands a legion that is 40-strong. He is one of the underworld's leading Behemoth fans. Even in his current weakened state, he won't leave until he has found her.","attack":"8300","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Amber","imagePath":"Amber.jpg","name":"Amber","form":"Original Form","number":21,"rarity":"4","caption":"Is there something important that you've lost? Let's go look for it.","defense":"7800","lore":"The soul of an automated doll made by the genius doll-maker, Abel. She is Doll No.3 in the hard-to-come-by Five Fragrances Series. She is currently owned by a certain agent.","attack":"7600","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Amber Magatama","imagePath":"Amber_Magatama.jpg","name":"Amber Magatama","form":"Original Form","number":22,"rarity":"3","caption":"(The magatama glows with a clear light...)","defense":"30","lore":"An enhanced magatama made from amber. Gives a huge XP boost to Anima spirits during fusion.","attack":"15","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Amber","imagePath":"Amber_HW.jpg","name":"Amber [HW]","form":"Halloween Form","number":23,"rarity":"4","caption":"I feel so happy and blessed! My life is like a dream come true!","defense":"7900","lore":"The soul of an automated doll made by the genius doll-maker, Abel. She is Doll No.3 in the hard-to-come-by Five Fragrances Series. Musk twisted her arm and got her to come to the Halloween Tower. ","attack":"7200","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Ame no Habakiri","imagePath":"Ame_no_Habakiri.jpg","name":"Ame no Habakiri","form":"Original Form","number":24,"rarity":"5","caption":"Show me a neck to be sliced!","defense":"6800","lore":"A legendary sword that appears in Japanese Mythology. Susano-o is said to have used this sword to slay Yamata no Orochi. Its blade shines with added luster when confronted by scaled monsters, such as dragons and snakes.","attack":"14500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Ameno Ohabari","imagePath":"Ameno_Ohabari_Ultimate.jpg","name":"Ameno Ohabari","form":"Original Form","number":25,"rarity":"5","caption":"Do inform me of any heads you want cut off.","defense":"5560","lore":"The soul of a divine blade that appears in Japanese mythology. It was used by Izanagi to slit Hinokagu-tsuchi's throat, and the blood that poured forth gave life to new gods.","attack":"13800","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Ameno Ohabari","imagePath":"Ameno_Ohabari.jpg","name":"Ameno Ohabari","form":"Ultimate Form","number":26,"rarity":"4","caption":"There is no being on earth I cannot cut through.","defense":"2650","lore":"The soul of a divine blade that appears in Japanese mythology. It was used by Izanagi to slit Hinokagutsuchi's throat, and the blood that poured forth gave life to new gods.","attack":"9200","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Ameno Tajikarao","imagePath":"Ameno_Tajikarao.jpg","name":"Ameno Tajikarao","form":"Original Form","number":27,"rarity":"4","caption":"If you look suspicious, you're coming with me.","defense":"8000","lore":"A gentle soul with a penchant for heavy labor, Ameno Tajikarao was employed at the Amaterasu Dance Party both as a security guard and on reception. He may look a bit on the gangly side, but he's the only one capable of unsealing Amano-Iwato cave. All in all, a crucially important behind-the-scenes player. ","attack":"11000","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Ameno Uzume","imagePath":"Ameno_Uzume.jpg","name":"Ameno Uzume","form":"Original Form","number":28,"rarity":"1","caption":"Coo-ey! Won't you come over here and dance with me?","defense":"1690","lore":"A goddess with extraordinary artistic talents. She is known for dancing in front of the cave that the sun goddess Amaterasu hid in, depriving the world of light.","attack":"1910","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Ameno Uzume","imagePath":"Ameno_Uzume_Focused.jpg","name":"Ameno Uzume [Focused]","form":"Halloween Form","number":29,"rarity":"5","caption":"Halloween's a great excuse for a party... I'm really getting into the mood!","defense":"14200","lore":"A goddess with extraordinary artistic talents. She heard there was a party going on, so decided to dress up and take a look for herself.","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Ameno Uzume","imagePath":"Ameno_Uzume_HW.jpg","name":"Ameno Uzume [HW]","form":"New Years Form","number":30,"rarity":"4","caption":"Happy new year! I look forward to another year of entertaining everyone with my dancing!","defense":"9400","lore":"A goddess with extraordinary artistic talents. She is keen to entertain the agents with her dancing at new year, and has chosen a special outfit in which to do so. She is always practicing in the hope of impressing Player.","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Ameno Uzume","imagePath":"Ameno_Uzume_New_Year.jpg","name":"Ameno Uzume [New Year]","form":"Focused Form","number":31,"rarity":"4","caption":"Hold on, Ammie! I'll have you out of there in no time!","defense":"9500","lore":"Uzume refers to Amaterasu by her lesser-known (and not quite as grand-sounding) sobriquet, Ammie. After Amaterasu shut herself up in Amano-Iwato cave again, Uzume tried to lure her out by performing a naked dance. When the dance proved to be a total bust, Uzume gathered her clothes and slunk away in shame. Word has it she spent the next several days with her head buried in a pillow. ","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Ancient Elf","imagePath":"Ancient_Elf_Ultimate.jpg","name":"Ancient Elf","form":"Original Form","number":32,"rarity":"4","caption":"Where are we going today? I hope it's somewhere fun!","defense":"9000","lore":"A type of fairy found deep in the forests of Europe. Brimming with curiosity, she loves to play tricks on people along with the High Elf. Though she doesn't show it, she is actually deeply insecure about her abilities as an ancient elf. ","attack":"9000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Ancient Elf","imagePath":"Ancient_Elf.jpg","name":"Ancient Elf","form":"Ultimate Form","number":33,"rarity":"3","caption":"This is my secret place. We can relax here. No one will find us!","defense":"6000","lore":"A type of fairy found deep in the forests of Europe. She feels very grateful towards Player, who aided her development, and is keen to offer her lap as a pillow whenever it's time for a nap in the forest. ","attack":"6000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Andromeda","imagePath":"Andromeda.jpg","name":"Andromeda","form":"Original Form","number":34,"rarity":"5","caption":"To think that you could win over a galaxy... I shall be needing to remain here and investigate your mysterious powers further...","defense":"3800","lore":"The soul of a galaxy 2.3 million light years away from Earth. She decided to come over here when Nyarlathotep disappeared, fearing the disturbance to the cosmic balance. She has struck up a strange friendship with Mira's Professor, Yata.","attack":"15000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Andromeda","imagePath":"Andromeda_Tanabata.jpg","name":"Andromeda (Tanabata)","form":"Tanabata Form","number":35,"rarity":"5","caption":"Sorry, but that area's off limits to you!","defense":"3800","lore":"A festival held in space was always going to need a big stellar hitter like Andromeda on board and, sure enough, she was a tireless member of the committee that organized it. The only breaks she took were to stuff her face with the treats and snacks kindly provided by Nyarlathotep. All her hard work has really paid off.","attack":"15000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Anima Magatama","imagePath":"Anima_Magatama.jpg","name":"Anima Magatama","form":"Original Form","number":36,"rarity":"4","caption":"(The magatama has a powerful glow...)","defense":"30","lore":"Enhanced Magatama. Gives an incredible XP boost to Anima spirits during fusion.","attack":"15","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Anne Corr","imagePath":"Anne_Corr.jpg","name":"Anne Corr","form":"Original Form","number":37,"rarity":"4","caption":"You're the luckiest sailor around, you know!","defense":"10750","lore":"The soul of an anchor, salvaged from the bottom of the ocean by Bonnie Anne. She is said to bring luck to whoever owns her, and is therefore desired by every pirate worth his salt. Player appears to be the one currently benefiting from the good fortune she brings.","attack":"5500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Anne Droid","imagePath":"Anne_Droid.jpg","name":"Anne Droid","form":"Original Form","number":38,"rarity":"3","caption":"It’s all…burnt…Processing failure...","defense":"4063","lore":"The soul of a cutting-edge maid android developed by a scientist. She’s just a prototype, and is still not great at carrying out orders.","attack":"5500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Antares","imagePath":"Antares.jpg","name":"Antares","form":"Original Form","number":39,"rarity":"4","caption":"I would do anything for you, even if it meant the world would end!","defense":"7200","lore":"Referred to as the \"heart of a scorpion\", Antares serves Scorpio and, as his betrothed, submits to her completely in all things. Her love burns with a dreadful fierceness. Her strengths lie in politics and maneuvering rather than combat. She is second to none when it comes to underhanded tricks.","attack":"9600","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Aoandon","imagePath":"Aoandon.jpg","name":"Aoandon","form":"Original Form","number":40,"rarity":"4","caption":"You're scared, you say? It's okay! Just carry on telling those stories. I'll be waiting right here by your side... Tee hee...","defense":"7800","lore":"A Japanese sprite who appears when you tell a hundred ghost stories in a row. She loves nothing more than scaring people, and is planning to give Mira a selection of her very favorite scary tales one of these days.","attack":"9500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Apple Bob","imagePath":"Apple_Bob.jpg","name":"Apple Bob","form":"Original Form","number":41,"rarity":"3","caption":"Come on! Hurry up and take a bite, will you?","defense":"6200","lore":"The ghost of traditional Halloween game of bobbing for apples. Under standard rules, the apples float on the water in a barrel while people try to bite it. This ghost has other idea, however, and she races off so quickly that the contest ends up resembling a long-distance running race. Her excuse for her behavious is that she feels sorry for the apples.","attack":"5400","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Aquamarine","imagePath":"Aquamarine.jpg","name":"Aquamarine","form":"Original Form","number":42,"rarity":"5","caption":"I wish them well on their voyage...","defense":"13500","lore":"The soul of a blue beryl gemstone, birthstone for March. She acts as a guardian for sailors, and her motherly smile is said to comfort those who voyage on the high seas.","attack":"13500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Aquila","imagePath":"Aquila.jpg","name":"Aquila","form":"Original Form","number":43,"rarity":"3","caption":"Yippeeee! Look out below!","defense":"7300","lore":"A ghost who harbors dreams of being able to soar freely through the sky. Her zodiac sign is the eagle, though this doesn't appear to have helped her realize her ambition. Recently, she spends most of her free time skydiving.","attack":"6500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Arcade Hermione","imagePath":"Arcade_Hermione.jpg","name":"Arcade Hermione","form":"Original Form","number":44,"rarity":"4","caption":"Fancy a ride? Hop on!","defense":"8500","lore":"The Anima of a full-size arcade cabinet who graced many a misspent youth in decades past. Loved by many for her tomboy disposition and grungy looks, this uber-slick biker chick won legions of male fans back in the day. Free from the commitments and everyday stresses of life, nowadays she devotes herself to long, relaxing drives in the country.","attack":"9400","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Arch-Daemon","imagePath":"Arch-Daemon.jpg","name":"Arch-Daemon","form":"Original Form","number":45,"rarity":"3","caption":"Will you offer up your spirit to me?","defense":"4980","lore":"An exceedingly powerful race of daemons. They are both highly-aggresive and love to show off.","attack":"6150","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Archangel","imagePath":"Archangel.jpg","name":"Archangel","form":"Original Form","number":46,"rarity":"3","caption":"Oh well. At times like this I suppose one has no choice but to serve humans...","defense":"3490","lore":"The eighth of the almighty archangels, and the leader of a host of divine messengers.","attack":"4010","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Arianrhod","imagePath":"Arianrhod.jpg","name":"Arianrhod","form":"Original Form","number":47,"rarity":"4","caption":"Oh, Titania... How many times do I have to tell you?","defense":"9100","lore":"A female goddess who appears in Celtic mythology. Her name means 'ring of silver'. She's good friends with Titania, but her strong sense of responsability means she's always getting her out of trouble.","attack":"9100","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Ariwara no Narihira","imagePath":"Ariwara_no_Narihira.jpg","name":"Ariwara no Narihira","form":"Original Form","number":48,"rarity":"4","caption":"Hey, Michizane. Check out that girl over there!","defense":"9600","lore":"A grandson of Emperor Heizei, and sometimes friend to Sugawara no Michizane. Despite being born of noble lineage, he's no stranger to vulgarity. Some people say that's just a sign that he's enjoying life, and living every day to the full. His cheeky grin would certainly attest to that!","attack":"7700","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Arko","imagePath":"Arko.jpg","name":"Arko","form":"Original Form","number":49,"rarity":"5","caption":"Name your target and I'll shoot it right down!","defense":"10000","lore":"The soul of Oberon's bow. The arrows fired from this magic-infused bow have never once failed to strike their target, but he only ever listens to what Oberon tells him to do.","attack":"10000","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Arondight","imagePath":"Arondight_Ultimate.jpg","name":"Arondight","form":"Original Form","number":50,"rarity":"5","caption":"I do whatever I can to help my master, Lancelot. If he tells me to kill you, then that is what I shall do.","defense":"13500","lore":"The soul of a sword that was much loved by its owner, the knight Lancelot from Arthurian legend. She adores Lancelot, and carries out her master's commands to the letter. She will not hesitate to cleave through anyone who stands in her master's way.","attack":"13500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Arondight","imagePath":"Arondight.jpg","name":"Arondight","form":"Ultimate Form","number":51,"rarity":"4","caption":"Your kindness could be fatal on the battlefield. You'd better stand behind me, for your own safety.","defense":"9500","lore":"The soul of a sword that was much loved by its owner, the knight Lancelot from Arthurian legend. Originally ordered to follow Player by Lancelot, she eventually became very fond of her new master, and now tags along of her own free will.","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Arsad Aldavi","imagePath":"Arsad_Aldavi.jpg","name":"Arsad Aldavi","form":"Original Form","number":52,"rarity":"4","caption":"There is no such thing as an undeserving life.","defense":"8290","lore":"A young and highly talented priest who has overseen the deaths and ascension to heaven of countless individuals. He is known for his slightly outmoded way of speaking. When it comes to protecting souls, purifying evil, and reincarnating the departed, this guy's in a league of his own.","attack":"7950","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Artemis","imagePath":"Artemis.jpg","name":"Artemis","form":"Original Form","number":53,"rarity":"5","caption":"Humanity, you should be under my protection, I'm telling you!","defense":"13980","lore":"The goddess of hunting and the moon. She was so impressed when man finally managed to walk on the moon that she rewarded humanity by sending all manner of gifts whizzing towards the surface of the Earth. But it turns out that a certain government agency decided that this stuff was too advanced for the Average Joe, and kept these cosmic offerings safely under lock and key.Artemis is seriously disappointed by this, and is waiting patiently for mankind to level up.","attack":"14250","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Asmodeus","imagePath":"Asmodeus.jpg","name":"Asmodeus","form":"Original Form","number":54,"rarity":"4","caption":"Wh-Who, me? Oh no, I couldn't possibly!","defense":"9500","lore":"A young girl from noble origins, this ghost's appearance puts one in mind of a pure and innocent lily... Which is ironic, because she's actually one of the least innocent ghosts you're ever likely to meet: Ladies and gentlemen, say hello to the Demon of Lust!","attack":"9500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Astaroth","imagePath":"Astaroth.jpg","name":"Astaroth","form":"Original Form","number":55,"rarity":"5","caption":"Hey, human! Consider yourself honored I'm letting you join my clan!","defense":"12200","lore":"One of the 72 demons from the Key of Solomon. One of Beelzebub's close affiliates, she was a duchess of Hell and led a forty-strong legion of spirits. She is said to have once lived in heaven. However, she flies into a rage if you bring the subject up, so watch what you say!","attack":"12550","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Azuki","imagePath":"Azuki.jpg","name":"Azuki","form":"Original Form","number":56,"rarity":"3","caption":"I sense bad energy coming from over there... Be careful, won't you?","defense":"4500","lore":"A shinto maiden at a historic shrine, she specializes in exorcising vengeful ghosts and curses. She's been friends with Kasumi, who works in the same shrine since childhood.","attack":"3500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Azukiarai","imagePath":"Azukiarai.jpg","name":"Azukiarai","form":"Original Form","number":57,"rarity":"3","caption":"Hee hee...Time to wash some azuki beans! Hoo hoo!","defense":"7300","lore":"A Japanese ghost famous for washing azuki beans in rivers. Even when she goes to the beach with her friends, it's not long before she disapears off somewhere to engage in a spot of scrubbing. She never leaves the house without a handful of her trusty beans.","attack":"8000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Azusa","imagePath":"Azusa.jpg","name":"Azusa","form":"Original Form","number":58,"rarity":"3","caption":"You're working, you say? No, how boring! I want you to play with me...","defense":"4700","lore":"She started out life as an ordinary pet cat, but over a period of many years, morphed into a cat sprite. She always seems to want to play when you're concentrating hard on work or internet games...","attack":"5300","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Baalberith","imagePath":"Baalberith.jpg","name":"Baalberith","form":"Original Form","number":59,"rarity":"4","caption":"Worthless is he who is unable to discern truth from lies.","defense":"7300","lore":"A knight who is well versed in all forms of deceit. She judges people solely on their ability to discern fact from fib. Generally speaking, she looks down on humans, believing them to be slaves to desire who are easily fooled. It'll take more than a human to prove a match for Baalberith's powers of deceit.","attack":"9300","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Babette Boo","imagePath":"Babette_Boo.jpg","name":"Babette Boo","form":"Original Form","number":60,"rarity":"4","caption":"Heh heh, did I scare you?","defense":"9800","lore":"A princess ghost who likes dangling upside-down from ceilings to frighten people. Recently, the boy she fancies told her he'd had it with her fooling around, so she's a bit more subdued than usual. She gets mad if you say her hair decorations look like the dangling hand-holds you find in trains.","attack":"9800","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Bag of Fujin","imagePath":"Bag_of_Fujin.jpg","name":"Bag of Fujin","form":"Original Form","number":61,"rarity":"5","caption":"Huh? Santa? Who's that?!","defense":"8700","lore":"The soul of a bag used by the wind god. The incarnation of a painting bya famous artist. When he is in a good mood, the wind god blesses the human world with fair winds, but blows a gale when he is angry. Because he carries a large sack, he's often mistaken for someone else when December comes around... He loves summer, and gets grumpy as autumn approaches. This usually manifests itself in the form of a typhoon or two.","attack":"13700","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Baku","imagePath":"Baku.jpg","name":"Baku","form":"Original Form","number":62,"rarity":"5","caption":"You had a nightmare, you say? Sounds like fun! Say, do you mind if I come round yours tonight?","defense":"14000","lore":"A mythical beast said to feast on bad dreams. It loves seeking out fresh nightmares, and often bursts into people's bedrooms at night.","attack":"12000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Bamboo Decoration","imagePath":"Bamboo_Decoration.jpg","name":"Bamboo Decoration","form":"Original Form","number":63,"rarity":"4","caption":"Want to get poked by my bamboo? It will bring you good fortune! I'm giving away free pokes to the first five lucky volunteers!","defense":"9500","lore":"The ghost of the bamboo part of a traditional Japanese New Year decoration. She loves to curl up with a cat and relax over the New Year holiday. But she likes getting cash even more. Nothing makes her more supremely happy than lining up and admiring all of her New Year tips. And a sharp bamboo stick greets anyone who tries to take them away!","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Bamboo Grove","imagePath":"Bamboo_Grove.jpg","name":"Bamboo Grove","form":"Original Form","number":64,"rarity":"3","caption":"Feast your eyes on this illusion!","defense":"4200","lore":"An Anima that dwells within a bamboo grove. Rumor has it that the bamboo spears sticking out of her back grow back as soon as they're picked. Ever since news got out that someone had found a hundred million yen nestled on her person, she's been inundated with opportunist voyagers desperate to make their fortune.","attack":"7100","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Bamboo Sprig","imagePath":"Bamboo_Sprig.jpg","name":"Bamboo Sprig","form":"Original Form","number":65,"rarity":"3","caption":"What do you think? Does it suits me?","defense":"4500","lore":"Decorative sprigs of bamboo are an indispensable part of the Tanabata festival. This ghost has a lot of responsibility on her shoulders, as she performs the vital role of carrying every festival-goer's heart-felt wishes to the Milky Way.","attack":"5700","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Banshee","imagePath":"Banshee.jpg","name":"Banshee","form":"Original Form","number":66,"rarity":"3","caption":"Sob sob... No, no... These are tears of joy, you know! It's okay for me to be here, right?","defense":"4200","lore":"A crying sprite that originates from Scotland. She now lives with an agent","attack":"4200","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Barbatos","imagePath":"Barbatos.jpg","name":"Barbatos","form":"Original Form","number":67,"rarity":"5","caption":"Oh, someone who can keep me entertained at long last! ...Yes, I'm talking about you, good Agent...","defense":"14250","lore":"One of the 72 demons from the Key of Solomon and one of hell's demonic nobles.  He is capable of directing people to hidden treasure. He likes anything that's funny, and his current favorite pastime is laughing at all the strangeness that can be found near Player.","attack":"11750","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Barbatos","imagePath":"Barbatos_Summer.jpg","name":"Barbatos [Summer]","form":"Summer Form","number":68,"rarity":"5","caption":"Ah, good Agent! Show me more trifles to amuse me!","defense":"14000","lore":"He's been away from the spotlight for quite a while, which he's none too happy about. He never tires of amusing himself with all the nutty events that occur whenever a ghost agent by the name of Player is around. He's looking out for an opportunity to get back in the story.","attack":"11250","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Barbetta","imagePath":"Barbetta_Ultimate.jpg","name":"Barbetta","form":"Original Form","number":69,"rarity":"2","caption":"Hey! Is it time for me to do my stuff?","defense":"2750","lore":"The soul of an Italian automatic pistol. Due to its excellent design, it was manufactured up to 1980. Barbetta responds readily to fusion and develops into an enhanced form.","attack":"3190","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Barbetta","imagePath":"Barbetta.jpg","name":"Barbetta","form":"Ultimate Form","number":70,"rarity":"1","caption":"Freeze! Put down the donut and no one'll get hurt!","defense":"1370","lore":"The soul of an automatic pistol, originating in Italy. The latest model, which is used by the US Army, can be held in the right or left hand with equal ease.","attack":"1510","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Basho","imagePath":"Basho.jpg","name":"Basho","form":"Original Form","number":71,"rarity":"4","caption":"It's a fine sky today... It puts me in the mood for a poem...","defense":"9500","lore":"Japan's most famous poet, known all around the world for his haiku. Or at least, that's what everyone thinks... In truth, he was an undercover detective in the Warring States period, who traveled to the Tohoku region of Japan at the instruction of the shogunate to spy on the Ise clan. The haiku he penned were all secret coded messages. His talent for deception is the stuff of legend. Admittedly he appears harmless at first, but it's all just a very clever guise...","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Basho Leaf Fan","imagePath":"Basho_Leaf_Fan.jpg","name":"Basho Leaf Fan","form":"Original Form","number":72,"rarity":"4","caption":"You call that a fire? One flutter and I shall blow it out like a candle's flame!","defense":"7500","lore":"A legendary fan that can whip up a gale force wind. Wielded by the Iron-Ribbed Fan Master who appears in the Chinese tale \"Journey to the West\". It likes to engage in battles with daemons who have mastered fire, in order to hone its own abilities.","attack":"8800","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Bath Pass","imagePath":"Bath_Pass.jpg","name":"Bath Pass","form":"Original Form","number":73,"rarity":"3","caption":"Do you have a bath pass?","defense":"3550","lore":"A ghost who works in a long-established hot springs inn. No one can enter the hot springs without her permission. Rumor has it that she uses a mysterious power to seal away in an unknown dimension any who dare to ignore her authority. \t\t\t\t","attack":"6150","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Battle Elephant Queen","imagePath":"Battle_Elephant_Queen.jpg","name":"Battle Elephant Queen","form":"Original Form","number":74,"rarity":"4","caption":"'KILL THEM! KILL THEM ALL!","defense":"9500","lore":"The ghost of the queen of a ferocious and uncivilized tribe. When she mounts her elephant steed, she feels like she has dominion over life and death and would happily spend her life in the saddle. She is not the most articulate woman in the world.","attack":"10500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Bayashi-5 (Miyabi)","imagePath":"Bayashi-5_Miyabi.jpg","name":"Bayashi-5 (Miyabi)","form":"Original Form","number":75,"rarity":"4","caption":"Come on everyone, let me hear you scream!","defense":"9500","lore":"Vocalist of Bayashi-5, the most popular idol group from the Heian period. Miyabi is a talented singer and dancer. He believes he's the hottest guy on the planet, and that all the girls are in love with him. Though not a bad guy per se, other men are fairly resentful of him. A true pop star, complete with that all-elusive X-factor.","attack":"9500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Bayashi-5 (Taiju)","imagePath":"Bayashi-5_Taiju.jpg","name":"Bayashi-5 (Taiju)","form":"Original Form","number":76,"rarity":"4","caption":"You've got to be kidding! Everyone but me? But I can act too!","defense":"8550","lore":"The drummer of the Heian period pop idol group Bayashi-5. The least famous member of Bayashi-5, Taiju is often teased for looking like a backing musician. He rarely receives requests for PR-related jobs, and is nervous about his future in the band as a result.","attack":"8100","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Bayashi-5 (Yuta) ","imagePath":"Bayashi-5_Yuta_Tanabata.jpg","name":"Bayashi-5 (Yuta) (Tanabata)","form":"Tanabata Form","number":77,"rarity":"4","caption":"It's time for us to take our greatest hit into space!","defense":"6000","lore":"A popular member of the pop group Bayashi-5. Though his job is to sing backing vocals and add woodwind flourishes, he actually has a bigger following than the lead singer, and has had offers to ditch his other band members and perform solo at this festival. He doesn't have a minute's rest, while Taiju and Miyabi seem to have plenty of time to put their feet up. It doesn't seem fair, somehow.","attack":"8000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Baz","imagePath":"Baz.jpg","name":"Baz","form":"Original Form","number":78,"rarity":"3","caption":"Say, how 'bout I fire off a couple o' missiles?","defense":"5610","lore":"The soul of a surface-to-air missile launcher that is carried on the shoulder. He uses a thermal infrared guidance system to ensure he always hits his target.","attack":"5355","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Baz","imagePath":"Baz_%252B%252B.jpg","name":"Baz ++","form":"Original++ Form","number":79,"rarity":"3","caption":"Say, how 'bout I fire off a couple o' missiles?","defense":"6600","lore":"The soul of a surface-to-air missile launcher that is carried on the shoulder. He uses a thermal infrared guidance system to ensure he always hits his target. Potential ability++: Bonus to Max. Attack and Defense Limit","attack":"6300","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Beatrice","imagePath":"Beatrice.jpg","name":"Beatrice","form":"Original Form","number":80,"rarity":"3","caption":"How are you, flowers? And how are you, sun?","defense":"5700","lore":"A beautiful and immortal young woman, taken to be one of the first ever 'idols'. A very pure young lady, she was brought up surrounded only by delightful things, and innocent to the world's grimier parts. As a result, she's a bit out of the loop when it comes to worldly affairs, but it doesn't seem to bother her. Her sustenance comes from all the men who are taken prisoner as soon as they lay eyes on her.","attack":"6300","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Befana","imagePath":"Befana.jpg","name":"Befana","form":"Original Form","number":81,"rarity":"5","caption":"I was told this was just going to be simple guard duty. Ah, well...","defense":"9870","lore":"The ghost of a witch from Italian folklore. She is trying to create the new category of \"mature ghost\" by intentionally putting on the air of a gentle, mild-mannered old woman. But she really doesn't need to go to all that trouble, because she is already considered to be over the hill by the other ghosts, to whom she gives advice.","attack":"12390","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Behemoth","imagePath":"Behemoth_Calm.jpg","name":"Behemoth (Calm)","form":"Calm Form","number":82,"rarity":"5","caption":"Oooh... Can I just have a little taste of that...?","defense":"9500","lore":"A monster that has risen from the underworld. She turned into a beast after eating sushi with too much wasabi. Best go easy on the green stuff next time... A big star both in the underworld and in the heavens, she now only has eyes for <Players's name>.","attack":"4500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Behemoth","imagePath":"Behemoth_Calm_Tanabata.jpg","name":"Behemoth (Calm) (Tanabata)","form":"Calm [Xmas] Form","number":83,"rarity":"5","caption":"Oooh... That cake is absolutely delicious... Say, today seems like a great day for us to stick together. What do you say?","defense":"13800","lore":"A huge monster that has risen from the underworld. If she gets too worked up she'll turn back into a enormous monster, so you'll need to keep an eye on her. She's something of a celebrity in both the underworld and the heavens, and receives a huge number of Christmas presents, but she claims that spending her time together with Player is the best gift of all.","attack":"10800","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Behemoth","imagePath":"Behemoth_Calm_Xmas.jpg","name":"Behemoth (Calm) [Xmas]","form":"Calm (Tanabata) Form","number":84,"rarity":"5","caption":"Heh heh... That looks delicious...","defense":"12500","lore":"For this beast with a bottomless pit for a stomach, the \"Interstellar Tanabata Festival\" is all about eating endless snacks from the countless stalls. The rumble of her tummy sends the stallholders into a blind panic as they struggle to cope with the demand. The Behemoth can't wait for next year... Its only hope is that the stalls stock up with even more candy.","attack":"4750","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Behemoth","imagePath":"Behemoth_Rage.jpg","name":"Behemoth (Rage)","form":"Rage Form","number":85,"rarity":"5","caption":"GRRRAAAOOOAAAAGRH","defense":"4500","lore":"A monster that has risen from the underworld. Once it has let off steam, it is said to leave people alone until it gets hungry. Player conquered it and gained its power.","attack":"13600","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Behemoth's Collar","imagePath":"Behemoth%2527s_Collar.jpg","name":"Behemoth's Collar","form":"Original Form","number":86,"rarity":"3","caption":"That's it! Straight to me, that's a good girl!","defense":"5950","lore":"The soul of a collar designed to keep Behemoth in check. Stern but kind-hearted, she always has Behemoth's best interests at heart. Normally she's able to handle Behemoth when she plays up, but this time seems different...","attack":"6050","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Belial","imagePath":"Belial.jpg","name":"Belial","form":"Original Form","number":87,"rarity":"5","caption":"Feast your eyes on true divinity! Welcome to pure evil!","defense":"10500","lore":"She may look like a beautiful and refined angel, but really she's anything but. A twisted character who thrives on human vices such as jealousy, hatred, and greed. She may be a fallen angel, but she's still a divine being: a divinely awful one, at that.","attack":"12000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Bell Inscription","imagePath":"Bell_Inscription.jpg","name":"Bell Inscription","form":"Original Form","number":88,"rarity":"4","caption":"Oh, I'm so sorry...","defense":"9500","lore":"The Anima of a inscription carved into a bell in a Buddhist temple. It reads \"HISTORY DRIVES THE PRESENT INTO ACTION.\" Although she's not done a single bad deed in her life, the darkness of all those who with whom she's been involved have given her a heavy heart. That the inscription has triggered off a huge battle hasn't helped her sense of guilt...","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Bendita","imagePath":"Bendita.jpg","name":"Bendita","form":"Original Form","number":89,"rarity":"5","caption":"Listen up, everyone! We're all pure at heart!","defense":"12100","lore":"The Anima of a saucer of holy water. A pure and innocent young girl, untainted by the evils of the world. The mysterious purity she emanates is said to cleanse even the basest and most vulgar of human vices.","attack":"8500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Benkei Musashibo","imagePath":"Benkei_Musashibo.jpg","name":"Benkei Musashibo","form":"Original Form","number":90,"rarity":"3","caption":"Never fear when I'm here! Leave the defense to me!","defense":"5925","lore":"A hero of the Heian period who served Yoshitsune. Dutiful to the end, he is famous for dying on his feet after being struck by numerous arrows.","attack":"6450","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Yukimura Sanada","imagePath":"Benmaru_Sanada.jpg","name":"Benmaru Sanada","form":"Original Form","number":91,"rarity":"4","caption":"YAAARGH! I'm gonna be the strongest of them all!","defense":"6030","lore":"A hero from the Sengoku period. Second son of the great commander Masayuki Sanada, Benmaru served under the warlord Shingen Takeda. Benmaru was the name he was called by as a child.","attack":"9050","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Benzaiten","imagePath":"Benzaiten.jpg","name":"Benzaiten","form":"Original Form","number":92,"rarity":"4","caption":"C'mon! Let me hear you shred that guitar!","defense":"8375","lore":"The goddess of music and the arts, and one of the seven lucky deities. Recently, her band Seventh Heaven has been active on the celestial tour circuit.","attack":"7420","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Beowulf","imagePath":"Beowulf.jpg","name":"Beowulf","form":"Original Form","number":93,"rarity":"4","caption":"Dragons, show yourselves!","defense":"9500","lore":"Held in the highest esteem by his fellow dragon-bashers. He hit the road as soon as he heard that dragons had appeared in Japan. Nothing prepared him for the sight of dragons and wannabe pop stars that awaited him, however. He is still not sure he will ever recover. He's lost his faith in the value of dealing with dragons.","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Bermuda Triangle","imagePath":"Bermuda_Triangle.jpg","name":"Bermuda Triangle","form":"Original Form","number":94,"rarity":"3","caption":"That's it, step into my vortex...","defense":"7150","lore":"The Phantom of a mysterious stretch of ocean long feared among seafarers. Asked why she continues to make people disappear, her only response is that she's sick of people cruising over the top of her head. She's only recently begun to express contrition for her various misdeeds.","attack":"5000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Berserker","imagePath":"Berserker.jpg","name":"Berserker","form":"Original Form","number":95,"rarity":"4","caption":"I laugh in the face of pain!","defense":"9200","lore":"A crazed warrior that appears in Norse mythology. Blessed with the divine protection of Odin, he fights to the bitter end.","attack":"9500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Beryl Magatama","imagePath":"Beryl_Magatama.jpg","name":"Beryl Magatama","form":"Original Form","number":96,"rarity":"3","caption":"(The magatama glows with a clear light...)","defense":"30","lore":"An enhanced magatama made from beryl. Use it in fusion to greatly boost the XP of Phantom spirits.","attack":"15","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Big Kite Zamashi","imagePath":"Big_Kite_Zamashi.jpg","name":"Big Kite Zamashi","form":"Original Form","number":97,"rarity":"5","caption":"Here comes a good wind!","defense":"9500","lore":"She rides a large kite, and is often mistaken for a ninja. That, however is not the case. She is actually a skilled martial artist. To make up for her relative disadvantage in strength, she hit upon a solution of using aerial attacks, and that is when she came up with the idea of the kite. She is also often mistaken for a man.","attack":"13350","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Bikuni","imagePath":"Bikuni.jpg","name":"Bikuni","form":"Original Form","number":98,"rarity":"5","caption":"So by becoming immortal, I got to meet you. It's funny how life turns out...","defense":"11100","lore":"A human who became immortal after eating mermaid flesh. After spending years looking for ways to die, she meets Player and her fate is sealed.","attack":"10250","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Bisque Doll","imagePath":"Bisque_Doll.jpg","name":"Bisque Doll","form":"Original Form","number":99,"rarity":"5","caption":"Excuse me, I heard there was a doll festival being held...","defense":"13200","lore":"A doll popular among ladies and daughters of nobility in 19th century Europe. Hearing about the Girls' Festival, she packed her bags and made the trip to the Far East, but now she's worried that she sticks out like a sore thumb... She's fairly down to earth for a princess. A tomboy, she can occasionally be heard cracking cheesy jokes.","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Bisque Doll","imagePath":"Bisque_Doll_Tanabata.jpg","name":"Bisque Doll (Tanabata)","form":"Tanabata Form","number":100,"rarity":"4","caption":"Is this the right way to wear a yukata?","defense":"10250","lore":"After feeling very out of place at the recent Girls' Festival, this doll ghost vowed to do her research before the \"Interstellar Tanabata Festival\". She has come impeccably dressed in a classy yukata that's simply brimming with Japanese style and elegance.","attack":"7750","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Bisque Doll","imagePath":"Bisque_Doll_Halloween.jpg","name":"Bisque Doll [Halloween]","form":"Halloween Form","number":101,"rarity":"5","caption":"Once summer ends, this is the next big event...","defense":"14800","lore":"In true high-rolling bourgeois style, her entire Halloween outfit is bespoke and hand-made. Rumour has it that her love for Japan is so strong that she is planning to build her own rustic retreat.","attack":"12500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Biwa Hoshi","imagePath":"Biwa_Hoshi.jpg","name":"Biwa Hoshi","form":"Original Form","number":102,"rarity":"5","caption":"Hear me! Hear the blind priest's song!","defense":"11300","lore":"A \"performing monk\" who travels the land, reciting the famed Japanese \"Tale of Heike. Recently, he has preferred to arrange his traditional songs in more contemporary rock styles. Apparently, he even has a fan club....","attack":"11500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Black Angel","imagePath":"Black_Angel.jpg","name":"Black Angel","form":"Original Form","number":103,"rarity":"2","caption":"I'm not lost, I swear! I'm just...um...going for a little walk.","defense":"2650","lore":"An angel who is very proud of her beautiful singing voice. Together with the Red Angel, she is searching for the White Angel and the Blue Angel. She just decided to go for a little walk on her own, (Or so she says...)","attack":"4400","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Black Cat","imagePath":"Black_Cat.jpg","name":"Black Cat","form":"Original Form","number":104,"rarity":"4","caption":"Meow! You know it's bad luck to see me, don't you?","defense":"11000","lore":"The ghost of a black cat who is rather put out by the fact that she is considered an ill omen. With her high profile at Halloween, she has been trying to reinvent herself and shed her image of social outcast. Sadly, though, she's such an iconic figure at this time of the year that she is still treated as a bringer of bad luck.","attack":"7500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Blood-Soaked Candy","imagePath":"Blood-Soaked_Candy.jpg","name":"Blood-Soaked Candy","form":"Original Form","number":105,"rarity":"4","caption":"How's about some bright red candy?","defense":"9500","lore":"A ghost who ingratiates herself to others by distributing candy dripping with blood. It's actually really delicious, but people are so perturbed by its appearance that they always pass on her generous offer. They're not really covered in blood. It's strawberry sauce.","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Blue Angel","imagePath":"Blue_Angel.jpg","name":"Blue Angel","form":"Original Form","number":106,"rarity":"2","caption":"Hmm? You mean to say...Tokyo and Kyoto are two different places?","defense":"2260","lore":"A divine messenger who is very proud of her beautiful singing voice. She appears to be looking for the White Angel, who set out in search of their leader, but is yet to return.","attack":"2060","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Blue Heron Fire","imagePath":"Blue_Heron_Fire.jpg","name":"Blue Heron Fire","form":"Original Form","number":107,"rarity":"4","caption":"Yes, indeed. Hot springs are a wonderful thing.","defense":"9500","lore":"An assistant manager at a hot springs inn. However, since she works night shifts, not many guests get to see her. Some diehard fans lurk around late at night hoping to catch a glimpse of her, but she always sniffs them out and reports them. The proprietress of the inn then puts a stop to it, making any attempt to see Blue Heron Fire fruitless.\t\t\t\t\t.","attack":"9500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Bo","imagePath":"Bo.jpg","name":"Bo","form":"Original Form","number":108,"rarity":"2","caption":"Now, if I manage to hit this apple, you have to stay with me all day, okay?","defense":"2350","lore":"The soul of a crossbow used in the west. Setting the arrows takes a while, but she sure can shoot down fruit from trees and share it with her favorite people.","attack":"2350","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Boastful Spirit","imagePath":"Boastful_Spirit.jpg","name":"Boastful Spirit","form":"Original Form","number":109,"rarity":"4","caption":"Kneel before me so that I may use you as a footstool!","defense":"7200","lore":"An embodiment of the purest arrogance that appears along with winter's chill in the air. An unadulterated snob of the highest order. No matter who you are or where you are, she will be sure to be looking down at you. But she can be so charming and adorable that there is never any shortage of people willing to be looked down upon by her.","attack":"9200","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Boeman 787","imagePath":"Boeman_787.jpg","name":"Boeman 787","form":"Original Form","number":110,"rarity":"4","caption":"Up and away to a brighter future!","defense":"8900","lore":"The Anima of a state of the art passenger jet. He's been stirring up quite a storm recently, but (perhaps because of his princely lineage?) he doesn't seem to be letting it get to his head. Blinged out with all the latest gadgets and boasting an eye-catching design, he never fails to turn heads wherever he goes.","attack":"9400","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Bonnie Anne","imagePath":"Bonnie_Anne.jpg","name":"Bonnie Anne","form":"Original Form","number":111,"rarity":"5","caption":"Come wi' me, an' I'll show ye what a seafarin' woman is made of!","defense":"12750","lore":"The Divina of a female pirate who is notorious throughout the Caribbean. Formerly a crew member of the ghost ship, Chaos, where she was renowned for being a crybaby. She has now sworn allegiance to Player.","attack":"8800","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Bonnie Anne","imagePath":"Bonnie_Anne_Tanabata.jpg","name":"Bonnie Anne (Tanabata)","form":"Tanabata Form","number":112,"rarity":"5","caption":"If it be sharp-shooting yer after, I'm yer woman!","defense":"13000","lore":"A pirate has finally made it into space. She's intent on putting every shooting range at the festival out of business with her dead-eye accuracy, before sailing away with her pirate ship full of booty.","attack":"8000","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Brekkie","imagePath":"Brekkie.jpg","name":"Brekkie","form":"Original Form","number":113,"rarity":"2","caption":"Wakey wakey, it's time to get up...I'm telling you, you'll be late otherwise.","defense":"1000","lore":"A goddess who oversees breakfast. She gets up early to prepare something delicious, then gently wakes you up with its tempting smell. The eldest of the three divine Meal Maidens.","attack":"3200","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Brenda","imagePath":"Brenda.jpg","name":"Brenda","form":"Original Form","number":114,"rarity":"3","caption":"I'm gonna keep on running. That's what Cliffy told me to do.","defense":"5750","lore":"The vengeful spirit of one of America's most wanted. Following a string of armed bank robberies with her accomplice Clifford, Brenda went on the run and became a danger to the public.","attack":"5000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Brigit","imagePath":"Brigit.jpg","name":"Brigit","form":"Original Form","number":115,"rarity":"5","caption":"Come to me when you're feeling tired of battling. I'll help you dissolve all those stresses and strains.","defense":"9200","lore":"One of three sisters, this Irish goddess looks after the harvest. She recognizes in you a great brilliance of spirit, and was so worried about you battling day in day out that she decided to come along with you.","attack":"7500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Brocken Spectre","imagePath":"Brocken_Spectre.jpg","name":"Brocken Spectre","form":"Original Form","number":116,"rarity":"4","caption":"Right! Leave all this to me...","defense":"9300","lore":"A natural phenomenon which appears as a great ring of rainbow-colored light. A keen and talented mountain climber, he does everything with great panache. Even serious problems are taken on readily and easily, a tendency which can sometimes cause new problems for people.","attack":"8200","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Brownie","imagePath":"Brownie.jpg","name":"Brownie","form":"Original Form","number":117,"rarity":"4","caption":"Right, where to let off steam next? This is kinda fun, right? Let's kick some tail!","defense":"7500","lore":"The anima of a heavy machine gun employed on numerous battlefields over the years. Though skilled at reading the enemy's movements, he has the unfortunate tendency to go wading into battle alone when he gets hot-headed.","attack":"10500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Bunchu","imagePath":"Bunchu_Chinese_New_Year.jpg","name":"Bunchu [Chinese New Year]","form":"Chinese New Year Form","number":118,"rarity":"5","caption":"Any enemy of my country is an enemy of mine!","defense":"11060","lore":"A warrior who rides a black unicorn and wields a golden whip. He is such a noble man that he never lost his loyalty to the emperor, even after the emperor's fall.","attack":"15500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Bunny Battler","imagePath":"Bunny_Battler.jpg","name":"Bunny Battler","form":"Original Form","number":119,"rarity":"3","caption":"Has anyone seen my precious Lunar Hare?","defense":"4200","lore":"A devoted and doting retainer, in the employ of Lunar Hare. In fact so passionate is his devotion to his mistress that he's incapable of doing anything without her. Kids these days, eh? No backbone.","attack":"6800","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Bunny Bazooka","imagePath":"Bunny_Bazooka.jpg","name":"Bunny Bazooka","form":"Original Form","number":120,"rarity":"4","caption":"Look at me like that again and I'll blast you into next week!","defense":"9500","lore":"An armed rabbit guard, with a penchant for shooting rice cakes from her trusty bazooka. Though they serve the same princess, she's a lot less devoted to her duties than Bunny Battler. Firing rice cakes from a bazooka might sound like a foolproof plan, but in reality, the freshly-baked aroma of her ammunition tends to alert enemies to her presence.","attack":"7500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Candle Master","imagePath":"Candle_Master.jpg","name":"Candle Master","form":"Original Form","number":121,"rarity":"4","caption":"Prepare to have your life extinguished!","defense":"9500","lore":"An evil spirit that has inhabited a castle lit by people praying for long and healthy lives. Get on his nerves, and he'll severely shorten your lifespan in the blink of an eye... His fellow ghosts secretly think his possession of this type of candle to be beyond the bounds of good taste.","attack":"9500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Canopus","imagePath":"Canopus.jpg","name":"Canopus","form":"Original Form","number":122,"rarity":"5","caption":"I'll protect you! If that doesn't make me a hero, I don't know what will...","defense":"13200","lore":"The brightest star in the Carina constellation. He constantly and proudly refers to himself as a hero, fashioning himself after the orthodox protagonists from the literary canon. He's also incredibly clumsy, and Sirius and Ypsilon always have to pick up his mess. One of these days, he intends to return the favor to his most beloved childhood pals. For the moment, however, he's set on making the most of the joys adolescence has to bring. ","attack":"11000","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Cao Cao's Armor","imagePath":"Cao_Cao%2527s_Armor.jpg","name":"Cao Cao's Armor","form":"Original Form","number":123,"rarity":"4","caption":"I'm a perfect fit for Lord Cao Cao, you see, and that's all that matters...","defense":"9800","lore":"The suit of armor always worn by the military officer Cao Cao when he was founding the Cao Wei nation during the Three Kingdoms Period. She's actually a young lady with an indomitable spirit. Allegedly, the mental scars she received from hearing about Cao Cao's endless string of different women hurt far more than the injuries she sustained during battle...","attack":"7500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Capricorn","imagePath":"Capricorn.jpg","name":"Capricorn","form":"Original Form","number":124,"rarity":"5","caption":"Endure the wrath of my demonic blade!","defense":"12140","lore":"One of twelve celestial spirits who rule over the world of constellations. A passionate follower of the way of the sword, she wields a demonic blade that draws on and sacrifices its user's vitality in exchange for increased potency. It is rumored that any ghost slain by this sword can neither attain nirvana nor be reincarnated. ","attack":"14320","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Capricorn","imagePath":"Capricorn_Fallen.jpg","name":"Capricorn [Fallen]","form":"Fallen Form","number":125,"rarity":"5","caption":"Coming up: a one-way ticket to Purgatory!","defense":"13900","lore":"The crazed incarnation of the power once sealed within Capricorn. Possessed by the soul of the Demon King, she is the living embodiment of all evil.","attack":"11050","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Carbuncle Garnet","imagePath":"Carbuncle_Garnet.jpg","name":"Carbuncle Garnet","form":"Original Form","number":126,"rarity":"5","caption":"You feel like catching me? Hah hah! Over here!","defense":"10000","lore":"An as-yet-unknown-life-form from South America. The gemstone on her forehead apparently brings luck and wealth to its bearer.","attack":"10000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Carol","imagePath":"Carol.jpg","name":"Carol","form":"Original Form","number":127,"rarity":"4","caption":"So where's the next party?","defense":"7500","lore":"A ghost who is invited to one party after another. She's known as the epitome of gorgeousness. Her sister-in-law's claim to fame is sharing drinks with Carol. Basking in her big sister's reflected glory, this sister-in-law loves being referred to as one of \"the Carol sisters.\" Carol lives by her own instincts and consequently has many fans. She never seeks anyone else's approval or regrets a thing.","attack":"7900","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Castela","imagePath":"Castela.jpg","name":"Castela","form":"Original Form","number":128,"rarity":"4","caption":"Agh...! So they've finally made their move! Master, I tell you, you are the ray of hope for this world!","defense":"8500","lore":"The soul of a gravity gun developed in top secrecy by a certain defense organization. Her orders have been to invade Akihabara and carry out an ondercover investigation of the area so she now goes about in maid uniform, even all Anima on the inside. This rather unusual figure is actually a gravity gun capable of protecting the world!","attack":"8500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Cat Sith","imagePath":"Cat_Sith.jpg","name":"Cat Sith","form":"Original Form","number":129,"rarity":"3","caption":"I'll catch my prey, then take a cat nap!","defense":"3768","lore":"A cat sprite originally from Scotland. He loves pranks, jokes and japes, and is always testing the tolerance of his best friend, the Cu Sith.","attack":"4670","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Cat Sith","imagePath":"Cat_Sith_HW.jpg","name":"Cat Sith [HW]","form":"Halloween Form","number":130,"rarity":"5","caption":"I'm sleepy. Do you mind if I curl up on your lap?","defense":"8000","lore":"A cat sprite originally from Scotland. He loves pranks, jokes and japes. He and his best buddy Cu Sith are inseparable.","attack":"8000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Catherine","imagePath":"Catherine.jpg","name":"Catherine","form":"Original Form","number":131,"rarity":"4","caption":"My costume's pretty original, huh? There's no way I can lose with this!","defense":"8000","lore":"A European princess who mistook the Girls' Festival for a fancy-dress contest. You've got to feel sorry for someone that determined to win a contest that doesn't even exist... Realizing her mistake, she got super embarrassed and decided to hide in the bathroom.","attack":"9800","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Chain Mail","imagePath":"Chain_Mail.jpg","name":"Chain Mail","form":"Original Form","number":132,"rarity":"4","caption":"Fear not! I will protect you!","defense":"8050","lore":"A rugged and steadfast companion. This Anima may not be showy, but he can always be relied upon to protect you on the battlefield. The problem is that he's very heavy, and has edged ever closer to becoming obsolete over the years. Nowadays, people prefer a nice, light vest. Now he's just a taciturn embittered relic from a previous time.","attack":"4000","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Chak","imagePath":"Chak.jpg","name":"Chak","form":"Original Form","number":133,"rarity":"1","caption":"Keep your distance! Come near me or my master, and you'll get sliced!","defense":"870","lore":"The spirit of a chakram, a throwing weapon from ancient India.. It spins through the air and can take out enemies from a distance","attack":"870","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Chang'e","imagePath":"Chang%2527e.jpg","name":"Chang'e","form":"Original Form","number":134,"rarity":"4","caption":"You'll take me back to earth, you say? How wonderful! Please do!","defense":"9500","lore":"A deity who is the subject of several stories in Chinese mythology. Ever since stealing a peach that grants immortality from Xi Wangmu, she has lived a lonely existence on the moon.","attack":"9300","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Chaos","imagePath":"Chaos_Calm.jpg","name":"Chaos (Calm)","form":"Calm Form","number":135,"rarity":"5","caption":"Yo ho ho! Weigh anchor for the seven seas!","defense":"8750","lore":"The Anima of a giant pirate ship that terrorized the seas in the ancient times. Though consider a legendary ship among the pirates, it was sunk in a storm. Once a long-forgotten ghost ship condemned to roam the oceans for eternity, she now sails in the name of Player.","attack":"8750","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Chaos","imagePath":"Chaos_Rage.jpg","name":"Chaos (Rage)","form":"Rage Form","number":136,"rarity":"5","caption":"Grrraaaaagh!","defense":"6000","lore":"The Anima of a giant pirate ship that terrorized the seas in the ancient times. Though consider a legendary ship among the pirates, it was sunk in a storm. Having once roamed the waves as a ghost ship, it now serves Player, who conquered it.","attack":"13650","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Cheshire Cat","imagePath":"Cheshire_Cat.jpg","name":"Cheshire Cat","form":"Original Form","number":137,"rarity":"4","caption":"Reality, fantasy...Who really cares? That's what I always say.","defense":"10100","lore":"A strange cat with a perpetual grin on his face. A friendly character with an undeniable gift for the gab, he can sometimes be a little too open, and often confuses people by speaking in riddles. He knows the effect he has on people, and even enjoys it.","attack":"8100","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Chestney","imagePath":"Chestney.jpg","name":"Chestney","form":"Original Form","number":138,"rarity":"3","caption":"Love? Romance? Utterly worthless.","defense":"8000","lore":"The Anima of a box used during the Edo period to store large quantities of coins. Rich as well as handsome, this chest is one charming character indeed. Oh, and he's clever as well. (Not that he, uh...paid us to write that or anything. Ahem.)","attack":"6050","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Chimera","imagePath":"Chimera.jpg","name":"Chimera","form":"Original Form","number":139,"rarity":"4","caption":"Ooh, I could really do with a rabbit's tail... Oh, and some swan's wings as well, come to think of it! They're going to be soon in next season.","defense":"10000","lore":"A monstrous creature from Grecian mythology comprised of the various parts of different animals. She's one of the three 'cherry-picking' monsters, and the most style savvy amongst them, with her eye forever on the latest fashions.","attack":"10000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Chiyo Shrine","imagePath":"Chiyo_Shrine.jpg","name":"Chiyo Shrine","form":"Original Form","number":140,"rarity":"4","caption":"Alright––who made Ameno Uzume cry!","defense":"9500","lore":"A well-meaning ghost whose intense affection for Ameno Uzume unfortunately ends up bordering on the suffocating. If needs be, Chiyo would travel the length and breadth of galaxies to look out for her beloved Ameno. In fact, she's probably one of the reasons Ameno Uzume grew up to be quite so sheltered...","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Chiyome Mochizuki","imagePath":"Chiyome_Mochizuki.jpg","name":"Chiyome Mochizuki","form":"Original Form","number":141,"rarity":"5","caption":"So long as I have your wishes in mind, Master, you shall continue to live on...","defense":"12900","lore":"As a veteran shrine maiden serving under Shingen Takeda, she trained up hordes of new female ninjas. Having lived a quiet life for a long time, she got wind of the truth about the Inscription Incident, and then set about planning an attack on the Ninja Village. Having seen her attempts, one legendary soldier was heard to say that, in being prepared to tirelessly carry out orders and fight for the honor of her Master for hundreds of years, she came closest of all to the spirit of the true ninja. The only comment she was heard to make on the occasion, though, was \"I need my bed now...","attack":"10700","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Chiyome Mochizuki","imagePath":"Chiyome_Mochizuki_Moon_Viewing.jpg","name":"Chiyome Mochizuki [Moon Viewing]","form":"Moon Viewing Form","number":142,"rarity":"5","caption":"O Master, when will you return...?","defense":"15500","lore":"She spends every waking moment waiting for the reappearance of Shingen Takeda, though he appears to be in no hurry. Until he rejoins her, she has vowed to devote herself body and soul to honing her powers. No one knows when her wait will finally end, and no one knows what her future holds in store.","attack":"14000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Cinderella","imagePath":"Cinderella_Summer.jpg","name":"Cinderella [Summer]","form":"Summer Form","number":143,"rarity":"5","caption":"I won't let this horrid sun burn my delicate skin!","defense":"14000","lore":"This summer's insane heat has driven Cinderella into parading around in her bathing suit, even in her own castle. You won't find her blindingly-white swimsuit in any catalog. It was made specially for her. Like her famous slipper, it's the perfect size for her and only she can wear it. Rumors of the swimsuit losing its beauty at midnight are total lies, no doubt spread by certain ugly sisters.","attack":"14000","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Cinnamon","imagePath":"Cinnamon.jpg","name":"Cinnamon","form":"Original Form","number":144,"rarity":"3","caption":"Say! Which age would you like to relive? Let's return to your childhood and play for a bit, shall we?","defense":"3600","lore":"The soul of an automated doll made by the genius doll-maker, Abel. She is Doll No.4 in the hard-to-come-by Five Fragrances Series. She is currently owned by a certain agent.","attack":"4000","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Alice","imagePath":"Classic_Alice.jpg","name":"Classic Alice","form":"","number":145,"rarity":"5","caption":"","defense":"14110","lore":"","attack":"11000","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Clifford","imagePath":"Clifford.jpg","name":"Clifford","form":"Original Form","number":146,"rarity":"3","caption":"Hey, I only rob banks 'cause they're there to be robbed. Now, you got anything valuable on you, kid?","defense":"5000","lore":"The vengeful spirit of one of America's most wanted. Following a string of armed bank robberies with his accomplice Brenda, Clifford went on the run and became a danger to the public.","attack":"5750","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Cloud Mirror","imagePath":"Cloud_Mirror.jpg","name":"Cloud Mirror","form":"Original Form","number":147,"rarity":"5","caption":"Gaze upon my surface Player, and who knows what you'll find! Heh heh!","defense":"14800","lore":"The spirit of an ancient mirror, it is said to reflect the true nature of any demon, faerie, or human who looks into it. Not to be confused with your altogether less mysterious companion Mira.","attack":"6000","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Coeurl","imagePath":"Coeurl_Summer.jpg","name":"Coeurl [Summer]","form":"Summer Form","number":148,"rarity":"4","caption":"Quail before your tiger overlord!","defense":"6060","lore":"A ghostly intergalactic apparition in the form of a tiger. Upon her arrival on earth, so fearful was she of wilting in the intense heat that the first thing she did was buy a new swimsuit. She decided to purchase a leopard-skin swimsuit as a way of respects to her late fellow felines. (Just to be clear, it was a leopard-skin print. It wasn't actually made from leopard's skin)","attack":"9500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Cordie","imagePath":"Cordie.jpg","name":"Cordie","form":"Original Form","number":149,"rarity":"3","caption":"I cannot be of service to you any longer. But I beg you, please don't throw me away...","defense":"6300","lore":"The soul of a black telephone that everybody used to have in their homes as standard. With a retro rotary dial pad, you only see specimens of its kind in antique shops these days.","attack":"6300","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Corona Australis","imagePath":"Corona_Australis.jpg","name":"Corona Australis","form":"Original Form","number":150,"rarity":"3","caption":"Hey, everybody needs to get away every now and then... Am I right?","defense":"4000","lore":"A constellation currently vacationing in the south. A sheltered girl from a good family, she has the means to travel the universe. Her unique perspective on the world often upsets those around her, however.","attack":"6500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Crane Wife","imagePath":"Crane_Wife.jpg","name":"Crane Wife","form":"Original Form","number":151,"rarity":"3","caption":"Brrr... I'm chilled to the very bone...","defense":"3800","lore":"The crane lady of Japanese folklore fame. Sensitive to the cold since birth, her naturally chilly constitution was further compounded by a near-death experience on a chilly mountain. Lately, however, she's very blasé about her experience, and even says frightening things like her specialty is to freeze people to death by touching them with her cold hands. ","attack":"4800","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Crayne","imagePath":"Crayne.jpg","name":"Crayne","form":"Original Form","number":152,"rarity":"4","caption":"Yoo-hoo! Doesn't this feel great? Let's see how high I can go today!","defense":"9200","lore":"The soul of a crane who works at a construction site. She loves the crisp, blue morning sky. Dedicated to her work, she's been known to reach heights inconceivable for most cranes.","attack":"6000","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Crystal Magatama","imagePath":"Crystal_Magatama.jpg","name":"Crystal Magatama","form":"Original Form","number":153,"rarity":"1","caption":"(The magatama glows gently...)","defense":"30","lore":"An enhanced magatama made from crystal. A mixer daemon perfect for fusing with Divina spirits","attack":"15","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Cthugha","imagePath":"Cthugha.jpg","name":"Cthugha","form":"Original Form","number":154,"rarity":"4","caption":"C'mon, you gotta get a bit hotter than that! If you don't start making an effort, I'm just gonna burn you...","defense":"9500","lore":"One of the Great Old Ones from the Cthulhu Mythos universe, whose body is cloaked in numerous flames. Arch enemy of the Evil Gods.","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Cu Sith","imagePath":"Cu_Sith.jpg","name":"Cu Sith","form":"Original Form","number":155,"rarity":"3","caption":"Listen to me howl three times... It will be the last thing you hear.","defense":"5225","lore":"A dog sprite that originates in Scotland. \"Cu\" is a Celtic term for \"dog\". She is best friends with Cat Sith.","attack":"4870","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Cu Sith","imagePath":"Cu_Sith_HW.jpg","name":"Cu Sith [HW]","form":"Halloween Form","number":156,"rarity":"4","caption":"If Player and Cat Sith are happy, then so am I!","defense":"8300","lore":"A dog sprite that originates in Scotland. \"Cu\" is a Celtic term for \"dog\". She is best friends with Cat Sith. She was responsible for organizing the Halloween Tower event.","attack":"7700","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Cyclops Dragon","imagePath":"Cyclops_Dragon.jpg","name":"Cyclops Dragon","form":"Original Form","number":157,"rarity":"4","caption":"Whatever you are trying to achieve, I will destroy...","defense":"9300","lore":"An unusual ghost, he was originally the name of a one-eyed hero, but developed a phantasmal life of his own. Insofar as he demands utter devotion from his followers, he's actually not all that far removed from being a pop star himself. If you really think about it, his clockwork mechanism somehow serves as a metaphor for the way stars manipulate people like puppets.","attack":"7500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Cyrca the Sylph","imagePath":"Cyrca_the_Sylph.jpg","name":"Cyrca the Sylph","form":"Original Form","number":158,"rarity":"3","caption":"So you're the one who's fascinated by the legendary wind... I've been waiting for you...","defense":"4400","lore":"A wind spirit and one of the Four Elements. She is the younger sister of Zephyr the Sylph. The pair are big troublemakers who are known affectionately by the other sylvan sprites as the silly siblings. When they join forces with Puck, there's absolutely no stopping them.","attack":"4400","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Daikokuten","imagePath":"Daikokuten.jpg","name":"Daikokuten","form":"Original Form","number":159,"rarity":"3","caption":"It's all about keeping rhythm!","defense":"4870","lore":"A goddess of good fortune and one of the seven lucky deities.  Daikokuten is responsible for bringing bountiful harvests.  She is celestially active as a member in a band called Seventh Heaven, and is Ebisu's childhood friend.","attack":"5255","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Daji","imagePath":"Daji.jpg","name":"Daji","form":"Original Form","number":160,"rarity":"5","caption":"Let me watch you squirm!","defense":"10200","lore":"A favorite concubine of King Zhou of the Shang Dynasty, Daji abused her claim to power for various nefarious ends. Many a foolish man fell victim to the combination of her false sincerity and voluptuous figure. However, not many would live to tell the tale.","attack":"12800","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Dance O'Matic","imagePath":"Dance_O%2527Matic.jpg","name":"Dance O'Matic","form":"Original Form","number":161,"rarity":"3","caption":"The only thing that makes up for a missed day's practice is...three extra days' practice!","defense":"4200","lore":"The ghost of a robot designed to aid dance training. Intended for those without easy access to a dancing partner, his old age and poor lubrication have sadly left him incapable of dancing anything besides \"The Robot\".","attack":"5900","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Dancing Doll","imagePath":"Dancing_Doll.jpg","name":"Dancing Doll","form":"Original Form","number":162,"rarity":"4","caption":"If you know where to look, there's no info you can't find on the web.","defense":"8900","lore":"You wouldn't know it from her youthful appearance, but this ghost is actually an extremely refined dancer. A devoted student of dance, she's reportedly got thousands of dance videos stored inside her tablet PC. When it comes to appraising her skills, she ignores accolades and others' opinions, instead relying solely on her own judgment. Seriously: how old is she, again? ","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Daphne","imagePath":"Daphne.jpg","name":"Daphne","form":"Original Form (Event)","number":163,"rarity":"4","caption":"My laurel leaves shall all be dedicated to you.","defense":"8150","lore":"A strikingly beautiful nymph from Greek mythology. Pursued by Apollo who was infatuated with her, she was transformed into a laurel tree.","attack":"5550","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Daphne","imagePath":"Daphne_-.jpg","name":"Daphne -","form":"Original Form","number":164,"rarity":"4","caption":"My laurel leaves shall all be dedicated to you.","defense":"8000","lore":"A strikingly beautiful nymph from Greek mythology. Pursued by Apollo who was infatuated with her, she was transformed into a laurel tree.","attack":"5400","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Dark Elf","imagePath":"Dark_Elf.jpg","name":"Dark Elf","form":"Original Form","number":165,"rarity":"3","caption":"I do miss the forest so very much.","defense":"5272","lore":"A type of fairy found deep in the forests of Europe. As well as protecting the forest, they also secretly come to the aid of humans tricked by High Elves.","attack":"7100","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Dark Night Dress","imagePath":"Dark_Night_Dress.jpg","name":"Dark Night Dress","form":"Original Form","number":166,"rarity":"4","caption":"No peeking, you naughty thing!","defense":"7500","lore":"A beguiling little witch with bewitching charms. She claims she can only come out at night, and that daylight doesn't agree with her. The truth, however, is that she's gotten herself into a bad routine. At Halloween parties, she usually drinks too much and ends up passing out.","attack":"7500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Dartz","imagePath":"Dartz.jpg","name":"Dartz","form":"Original Form","number":167,"rarity":"1","caption":"Ready... Steady... Go for it!","defense":"1920","lore":"This spirit embodies the game of darts. She came into being when the game was invented five centuries ago, when soldiers would kill time by throwing arrows at wine barrels.","attack":"2400","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Deadshot Dmitri","imagePath":"Deadshot_Dmitri.jpg","name":"Deadshot Dmitri","form":"Original Form","number":168,"rarity":"4","caption":"There is nowhere to run, and nowhere to hide","defense":"9500","lore":"The Anima of a sniper's rifle. This formidable warrior boasts a faultless record of getting his man. He boasts unparalleled powers of concentration, and can lie in wait for his target for days on end without food or water. He enjoys a well-earned slug of vodka after every successful operation. ","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Delphyne","imagePath":"Delphyne.jpg","name":"Delphyne","form":"Original Form","number":169,"rarity":"4","caption":"I cannot go against my sister's orders!","defense":"9000","lore":"The Phantom younger sister of Typhon. Cruel by nature, she devotes herself entirely to the destructive impulses that well up inside her. She is always breaking things, and nothing lasts long in her possession. This Phantom is rather a nuisance.","attack":"9000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Motochika","imagePath":"Demon_Motochika.jpg","name":"Demon Motochika","form":"Original Form","number":170,"rarity":"5","caption":"No! Chika wants to go home and play with toys!","defense":"9500","lore":"A hero from the Sengoku period. A weak and sickly child, he was nicknamed the Princess. However, he would later rise to become ruler of Shikoku.","attack":"10800","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Deneb","imagePath":"Deneb.jpg","name":"Deneb","form":"Original Form","number":171,"rarity":"4","caption":"Climb on my back and hold on tight. We're going on an interstellar voyage!","defense":"9000","lore":"One of the vertices of the Summer Triangle. A stellar deity of the Cygnus constellation. She shines brightly in the nether regions of the Cygnus swan.","attack":"8300","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Deneb Algedi","imagePath":"Deneb_Algedi.jpg","name":"Deneb Algedi","form":"Original Form","number":172,"rarity":"4","caption":"Chaos. Destruction. Mayhem.","defense":"7910","lore":"A ghost who harbors within her the seeds of unfettered brutality. Her insatiable thirst for blood accelerated her evolution into the lethally efficient hunter she is today.","attack":"9980","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Devoted Chimp","imagePath":"Devoted_Chimp.jpg","name":"Devoted Chimp","form":"Original Form","number":173,"rarity":"3","caption":"No one can outwit my traps!","defense":"4700","lore":"Faithful companion and trusted sidekick to the legendary hero Momotaro. A creative thinker, he specializes in devising intricate traps and devices with which to take out his opponents. He has a delicate relationship with Faithful Hound, who loves to wind him up. He lives for the sweet taste of victory, and will stop at nothing to get what he wants.","attack":"6700","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Diamond Dragon","imagePath":"Diamond_Dragon.jpg","name":"Diamond Dragon","form":"Original Form","number":174,"rarity":"5","caption":"Grrraaaaaargh!","defense":"12900","lore":"The Dragon Princess's bodyguard. The evil energy he has encountered in Japan has driven him into a frenzied state. He is now intent on causing all kinds of trouble. However, his behavior has somehow set the dragon princess on the path to pop stardom, so maybe everything has worked out for the best. Influenced by his princess, this dragon has become quite the pop aficionado. He even sleeps hugging a cuddly pop star doll, or so it is said.","attack":"14400","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Diamond Dust","imagePath":"Diamond_Dust.jpg","name":"Diamond Dust","form":"Original Form","number":175,"rarity":"5","caption":"Come into my freezing embrace!","defense":"10030","lore":"A snow queen with a frosty demeanor that can turn a town into a tundra in a heartbeat. Her appearance is always accompanied by a precipitous drop in temperature which freezes the water vapor in the air and makes everything all sparkly and shiny. But no matter how beautiful you think she is, don't get too close, or you'll end up as a human ice pop.","attack":"14400","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Diamond Magatama","imagePath":"Diamond_Magatama.jpg","name":"Diamond Magatama","form":"Original Form","number":176,"rarity":"5","caption":"The magatama glows with an inner light...","defense":"30","lore":"(The magatama glows with an inner light...) An enchanced magatama made from diamond. Gives an incredible XP boost to Divina during fusion.","attack":"15","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Diaochan","imagePath":"Diaochan.jpg","name":"Diaochan","form":"Original Form","number":177,"rarity":"3","caption":"Nothing brings me greater happiness than being in your service.","defense":"6470","lore":"One of the Four Beauties of Ancient China.  Diaochan appears in the novel 'Romance of the Three Kingdoms', where she uses her beauty to turn Dong Zhuo and Lu Bu against each other.","attack":"5218","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Dinnie","imagePath":"Dinnie.jpg","name":"Dinnie","form":"Original Form","number":178,"rarity":"2","caption":"Honey, you've got mustard on your cheek!","defense":"3200","lore":"A goddess who oversees dinner. She's always got a meal ready for when her master gets home. The youngest of the divine Meal Maidens.","attack":"1000","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Divina Magatama","imagePath":"Divina_Magatama.jpg","name":"Divina Magatama","form":"Original Form","number":179,"rarity":"4","caption":"(The magatama has a powerful glow...)","defense":"30","lore":"Enhanced Magatama. Gives an incredible XP boost to Divina spirits during fusion.","attack":"15","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Dj Yo-kai","imagePath":"Dj_Yo-kai.jpg","name":"Dj Yo-kai","form":"Original Form","number":180,"rarity":"4","caption":"Can I get a Yo to the Kai?","defense":"9500","lore":"An up-and-coming DJ who's famous around all the trendiest hipster ghost joints. She's got the whole teeny-bopper chic \"thang\" down to a T. Rumor has it she's often seen frequenting swanky grown-up social functions, leading some to wonder whether she's actually pretending to be younger than she really is. Her sublime DJ performances suggest someone who's been around the block more than once or twice, lending further credence to the age-doctoring theories.","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Dojigiri","imagePath":"Dojigiri.jpg","name":"Dojigiri","form":"Original Form","number":181,"rarity":"5","caption":"No need to worry when I'm around. I'll silence all those whining brats!","defense":"13600","lore":"One of the five heavenly swords. Yoritomo used this sword to decapitate Shuten-doji. It seems the presence of this sword stops children crying at night. She values personal relationships so highly, she believes they are the only thing that cannot be cut.","attack":"14000","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Dojigiri","imagePath":"Dojigiri_Mt._Fuji.jpg","name":"Dojigiri [Mt. Fuji]","form":"Summer Form","number":182,"rarity":"5","caption":"Gah! Does it have to be quite so hot?","defense":"12950","lore":"This heavenly sword spirit is finding the summer heat tough to handle. She has come to the ocean to try and cool down a bit. She's worried about rusting in the salty sea air, so is careful to shower every time she changes.","attack":"14700","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Dojigiri","imagePath":"Dojigiri_Summer.jpg","name":"Dojigiri [Summer]","form":"Mt. Fuji Form","number":183,"rarity":"5","caption":"Let's make this another great year (mumble, mumble)... Zzz...","defense":"13200","lore":"In Japan, dreaming of Mt. Fuji on New Year's Eve is considered lucky. In Dojigiri's dream, she greeted her friends under a clear winter sky, with Mt. Fuji in the distance. She can hardly contain her excitement at this auspicious start to the new year: \"Something big is going to happen this year. I can just feel it!","attack":"14900","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Dollmaker Phee","imagePath":"Dollmaker_Phee.jpg","name":"Dollmaker Phee","form":"Original Form","number":184,"rarity":"4","caption":"Dolls... I l-love dolls... Heh.","defense":"9500","lore":"A mad scientist-like character with a talent for creating creepily lifelike dolls. He is obsessed with making dolls that look like his first love, Bianca. He carries around his favorite creation on his shoulder. After hearing that dolls were part of the Girls' Festival festivities, he made a beeline for the EX Girls' Festival venue.","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Doppelgänger","imagePath":"Doppelg%25C3%25A4nger.jpg","name":"Doppelgänger","form":"Original Form","number":185,"rarity":"5","caption":"I am you, and you are me...","defense":"9500","lore":"A person's evil twin, physically identical to them in every way. It's said that seeing your own doppelgänger is a sign that your death is near. (Mirrors probably don't count.)","attack":"13600","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Dora","imagePath":"Dora_ANNV.jpg","name":"Dora [ANNV]","form":"Character","number":186,"rarity":"5","caption":"Hand over your rare daemons to me!","defense":"12250","lore":"A bounty hunter who can see spirits like the ghost agents. She collects rare Daemons to sell for huge amounts of money. In order to capture ghosts, Dora chants a spell, but her spell does not seem to work on strong Divina spirits. Her Daemons are Hemera (Ultimate) and Nyx (Ultimate). First appears in Chapter Five as an antagonist, but later becomes your ally. The last time she is seen is in Chapter: Eight, where she was aiming to capture many of the awakened Spirits.","attack":"14550","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Doton no Jutsu","imagePath":"Doton_no_Jutsu.jpg","name":"Doton no Jutsu","form":"Original Form","number":187,"rarity":"4","caption":"Here's mud in your eye!","defense":"8800","lore":"A Phantom who utilizes the earth in his secret ninja techniques. Still just a kid, he loves nothing better than stirring things up. He's the head of the shock troop of three ghosts who have sprung from ninja techniques. He was born to make trouble.","attack":"9000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Dracula","imagePath":"Dracula.jpg","name":"Dracula","form":"Original Form","number":188,"rarity":"5","caption":"Of course I'll lend you some of my powers! In exchange for a quick bite of your neck...","defense":"10101","lore":"A vampiric earl who reatins his youthful appearance by sucking the blood of humans. Contrary to his stern but beautiful appearance, he is famed for the gentlemanly way he lures people into his castle. He is particularly fond of super hot Mala hot-pots.","attack":"13831","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Dragon Princess","imagePath":"Dragon_Princess.jpg","name":"Dragon Princess","form":"Original Form","number":189,"rarity":"5","caption":"Witness the greatest star in pop history!","defense":"7000","lore":"Though hardly befitting one of such noble blood, this dragon was won over by a pop star she witnessed in her youth, and ever since, she has set her sights on being the biggest star on the planet. Naturally, her parents weren't supportive at first, but they soon changed their tune when she became famous. Now they're her biggest fans. But isn't that always the way? She works tirelessly to take her rightful place as the world's biggest star.","attack":"14500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Dragon Princess","imagePath":"Dragon_Princess_Halloween.jpg","name":"Dragon Princess [Halloween]","form":"Halloween Form","number":190,"rarity":"5","caption":"How dare you ruin my performance?!","defense":"9500","lore":"A noble dragon who plans on becoming the greatest star in pop history. She was hired to perform the opening number at the Halloween party, but was interrupted by the Pumpkin Kings [Wild] and didn't get to sing a single note. She battles alongside you-not so much because she cares about the Halloween party, but more because she wants her chance on stage back.","attack":"13300","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Dragonslayer","imagePath":"Dragonslayer.jpg","name":"Dragonslayer","form":"Original Form","number":191,"rarity":"4","caption":"Save for the bonds that bind people together, there is nothing my blade cannot sever.","defense":"9500","lore":"The spirit of a giant sword that can pierce dragons' adamantine scales. After receiving a request from the Ghost Guild, this ghost came to fight against the dragons, but has been flummoxed by the sheer scale of pop star enthusiasm it has run into.","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Dreadnought Dorothy","imagePath":"Dreadnought_Dorothy.jpg","name":"Dreadnought Dorothy","form":"Original Form","number":192,"rarity":"4","caption":"Aim.. Fire!","defense":"7200","lore":"A British battleship optimized for long range naval combat, this dreadnought was truly revolutionary in her day. Her devastating firepower and the impressive figure she struck upon the ocean led to an entire generation of battleships being named after her.","attack":"8900","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Drum of Raijin","imagePath":"Drum_of_Raijin.jpg","name":"Drum of Raijin","form":"Original Form","number":193,"rarity":"5","caption":"That Bag of Fujin needs to put some clothes on. I can see everything!","defense":"9200","lore":"The soul of a drum used by the thunder god. The incarnation of a painting by a famous artist. Despite their many differences, she is inseparable from Fujin, and they have been companions for a long time. She is neat and dignified, but has recently realized that she wants Fujin to be more than just her companion. As a result she gets nervous in his presence, and unleashes a blast of lightning. She cannot stand humans.","attack":"13400","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Ebisu","imagePath":"Ebisu.jpg","name":"Ebisu","form":"Original Form","number":194,"rarity":"3","caption":"See? I told you this would be exciting!","defense":"5255","lore":"A goddess of good fortune and one of the seven lucky deities. Ebisu is responsible for prosperity in business. She is celestially active as a member of a band called Seventh Heaven, and is Daikokuten's childhood friend.","attack":"4870","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Elixir of Life","imagePath":"Elixir_of_Life.jpg","name":"Elixir of Life","form":"Original Form","number":195,"rarity":"5","caption":"Coming up: one arrow, straight from my bow to your heart!","defense":"10290","lore":"An Anima who rules over all vitality. It's said that anyone pierced by her arrows will inherit the gift of eternal life. We'll leave you to decide whether or not eternal life is the kind of gift you'd be lucky to receive...","attack":"13800","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Elizabeth Báthory","imagePath":"Elizabeth_B%25C3%25A1thory.jpg","name":"Elizabeth Báthory","form":"Original Form","number":196,"rarity":"4","caption":"Ah, I grow tired of the Iron Maiden. Today, my victims shall suffer the Brazen Bull!","defense":"7200","lore":"The ghost of an infamous serial killer of the Middle Ages. In her quest for fresh blood, she is said to have slaughtered countless young women in her fearsome career. The most terrifying thing of all is that she believes her actions to have been entirely reasonable.","attack":"9200","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Emerald Magatama","imagePath":"Emerald_Magatama.jpg","name":"Emerald Magatama","form":"Original Form","number":197,"rarity":"5","caption":"The magatama glows with an inner light...","defense":"30","lore":"(The magatama glows with an inner light...) An enchanced magatama made from emerald. Gives an incredible XP boost to Anima during fusion.","attack":"15","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Emperor Hadrian","imagePath":"Emperor_Hadrian.jpg","name":"Emperor Hadrian","form":"Original Form","number":198,"rarity":"4","caption":"So this is the famed Japanese style, eh?","defense":"9700","lore":"Emperor Hadrian was snoozing in his bath at home, when all of a sudden, he found himself transported to a Japanese inn. It may sound impossible, but apparently that sort of thing was par for the course in ancient Rome. At least, it was according to a certain popular Japanese comic book... ","attack":"8500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Emperor Napoleon","imagePath":"Emperor_Napoleon_Hot_Springs.jpg","name":"Emperor Napoleon [Hot Springs]","form":"Hot Springs Form","number":199,"rarity":"5","caption":"Hmm. The female body is a thing of mystery...","defense":"10060","lore":"Is it an act of karma that Napoleon Bonaparte, French revolutionary hero, ended up this way? In the spirit of democracy, he has abandoned his middle-aged paunch in exchange for a form more aesthetically pleasing to the masses: namely, that of a pretty lady. Although he barely sleeps, he doesn't feel so tired because he bathes a lot. ","attack":"13050","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Emperor Nero","imagePath":"Emperor_Nero.jpg","name":"Emperor Nero","form":"Original Form","number":200,"rarity":"5","caption":"Is anything more beautiful than destruction and despair?","defense":"8800","lore":"The vengeful spirit of the fifth Roman Emperor. Though he was a highly-cultured youth, he became a despot sullied with countless bloody deeds.","attack":"12050","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Emperor Wulie","imagePath":"Emperor_Wulie_Summer.jpg","name":"Emperor Wulie [Summer]","form":"Summer Form","number":201,"rarity":"5","caption":"Ah, so this is how you slip into a swimsuit.","defense":"9000","lore":"Regardless of the feelings of his wife and children, his overwhelming desire to learn the secrets of the female form has led him to his new lifestyle. His real name is Sun Jian. His decision to appear as a woman before his daughter, and enjoy it thoroughly, has led to certain rifts in his familial relations.","attack":"13200","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Emperor of Time","imagePath":"Emperor_of_Time.jpg","name":"Emperor of Time","form":"Original Form","number":202,"rarity":"5","caption":"Why won't Kaguya Hime turn to look at me...?","defense":"11500","lore":"An emperor who has fallen head over heels with Kaguya Hime. Inferior in might only to a god, he's a little unused to not getting his own way. His innate and almighty aura causes people to quake in fear whenever they come near him. That said, his ability to command thunder at will usually discourages anyone from even trying...","attack":"14300","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Emperor of the Night","imagePath":"Emperor_of_the_Night.jpg","name":"Emperor of the Night","form":"Original Form","number":203,"rarity":"5","caption":"What I wouldn't give for a set of wheels like that!","defense":"13750","lore":"He might look like a lovable fluffy sugary cake, but it turns out he is the devilish overlord of the night, a lover of carousing in the parts of town that never sleep. He dedicates his whole life to extravagance, excess and indulging his wanton whims.","attack":"13750","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Enchanted Apple Tree","imagePath":"Enchanted_Apple_Tree.jpg","name":"Enchanted Apple Tree","form":"Original Form","number":204,"rarity":"2","caption":"Heh heh. Like the look of this sword, do you?","defense":"3000","lore":"The spirit of an apple tree that was entrusted with a holy sword by the gods. She is more commonly known as Barnstokkr. She doesn't discriminate between good and evil, and watches over each and every challenger with a smile.","attack":"3500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Experimental Animal Catherine","imagePath":"Experimental_Animal_Catherine.jpg","name":"Experimental Animal Catherine","form":"Original Form","number":205,"rarity":"4","caption":"Okay, what am I?","defense":"7500","lore":"A dyed-in-the-wool animal lover, Catherine's fervent wish to become one herself was granted, and she awoke one day as a conglomeration of a variety of different species. Even so, she's remained strangely upbeat, enjoying the ability to experience defining characteristics of several animals all at once. One of the most positive-thinking ghosts you're ever likely to meet.","attack":"9500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Exusiai","imagePath":"Exusiai.jpg","name":"Exusiai","form":"Original Form","number":206,"rarity":"4","caption":"DIIIIIEEEE! YOU WILL ALL DIIIIEEEE!","defense":"7200","lore":"An angel on the front line in the battle that rages in heaven between the forces of good and evil. It is a brutal and bloody conflict that leaves no room for mercy. The forces of evil have cast their baneful shadow over scores of angels and driven them mad. This unfortunate spirit is angelic in nature, but the horror she has witnessed has fractured her fragile grasp on sanity.","attack":"7800","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Eyeleen","imagePath":"Eyeleen.jpg","name":"Eyeleen","form":"Original Form","number":207,"rarity":"4","caption":"Heh heh... Wanna see my cursed eye?","defense":"6500","lore":"A fashion-conscious teenager with a penchant for the rebellious eye-patch look. It looks like she's only got one eye, but only she knows what lies behind the bandage... It's a bit like Schrodinger's cat theory, if you think about it. (Look it up if you don't believe us!)","attack":"9300","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Faithful Hound","imagePath":"Faithful_Hound.jpg","name":"Faithful Hound","form":"Original Form","number":208,"rarity":"3","caption":"Think you can keep up with me, huh?","defense":"4600","lore":"Faithful companion and trusted sidekick to the legendary hero Momotaro. A gifted sprinter and fighter, she's also incredibly obedient and (whisper it) a little on the dim side. Watch you don't fall for her cute looks: she packs a mean bite!","attack":"6200","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Fang","imagePath":"Fang.jpg","name":"Fang","form":"Original Form","number":209,"rarity":"3","caption":"Right! Let's see about putting an end to these evil spirits!","defense":"4970","lore":"The soul of the dragon sword received by shogun Yorimasa as a reward for slaying the legendary Nue beast.","attack":"6280","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Fenrir","imagePath":"Fenrir.jpg","name":"Fenrir","form":"Original Form","number":210,"rarity":"3","caption":"I will devour Odin with a single bite.","defense":"6530","lore":"A mounstrous wolf from Norse mythology. Prophesied to bring about disaster for the gods, Odin, the god of war, ordered that she should be imprisoned.","attack":"5283","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Ferris","imagePath":"Ferris.jpg","name":"Ferris","form":"Original Form","number":211,"rarity":"1","caption":"If you’re looking for a fight, then look no further!","defense":"2800","lore":"The soul of a heavy-duty iron knuckle duster, Ferris boasts a brutally effective attack. It puts it to good use fighting other gang members.","attack":"2060","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Festive Firefighter","imagePath":"Festive_Firefighter.jpg","name":"Festive Firefighter","form":"Original Form","number":212,"rarity":"4","caption":"Witness the traditional art of firefighting!","defense":"5400","lore":"An event peculiar to Japan is the New Year parade of firefighters. This ghost is always there, getting into the spirit of the tradition. Other ghosts flock to see his death-defying, eyebrow-singeing display of firefighting skills.","attack":"7550","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Fiorella Kitano","imagePath":"Fiorella_Kitano.jpg","name":"Fiorella Kitano","form":"Original Form","number":213,"rarity":"4","caption":"Let us dine among the fragrant plum blossom...","defense":"8910","lore":"The soul of a plum tree that stands in Kyoto. She and her sister Fleur  once ran amok around the streets of Kyoto, incurring the anger of Sakura Sumizome.","attack":"6300","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Fir Tree Sprite","imagePath":"Fir_Tree_Sprite.jpg","name":"Fir Tree Sprite","form":"Original Form","number":214,"rarity":"4","caption":"Hee hee hee! I look pretty cute, wouldn't you say?","defense":"6110","lore":"A sprite born from a festive fir tree. She loves being draped in flashing lights, and is insanely enthusiastic about anything remotely shiny. If it's gaudy, glitzy or garish, you can rest assured that she's all over it. No one gives her the time of day once January rolls around, so she has to take her chance to show off while she can.","attack":"8200","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Fire Mistress","imagePath":"Fire_Mistress.jpg","name":"Fire Mistress","form":"Original Form","number":215,"rarity":"4","caption":"There isn't anything that I can't burn! Aha ha ha!","defense":"7030","lore":"The spirit of a flame, who uses scrolls and markers to create fires. She is frank and open-minded, an elder-sister type, who always advises people to keep their chin up whenever they are worrying about something. She tends not to think about anything too deeply and deals with life as it comes - an approach for which she is widely admired. She is the Water Mistress's twin sister. ","attack":"9200","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Fire Rat's Robes","imagePath":"Fire_Rat%2527s_Robes.jpg","name":"Fire Rat's Robes","form":"Original Form","number":216,"rarity":"4","caption":"How d'ya like that burn?!","defense":"9500","lore":"This hot-blooded, fiery-eyed young lady hails from ancient India. A skilled brawler, the air friction caused by the flurry of punches and kicks she rains down upon her opponents have been known to produce sparks.","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Flamberge","imagePath":"Flamberge.jpg","name":"Flamberge","form":"Original Form","number":217,"rarity":"5","caption":"Come fireflies, enter my blade, grant me protection!","defense":"11500","lore":"The soul of a Japanese sword. It is protected by insects. Even when the blade is damaged, hundreds of fireflies swarm to repair it, ensuring it stays sharp for eternity.","attack":"11050","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Flame Sprite","imagePath":"Flame_Sprite.jpg","name":"Flame Sprite","form":"Original Form","number":218,"rarity":"4","caption":"I'm so...hungry...","defense":"6300","lore":"A mysterious ghost who can often be seen flying through the air. Apparently, she appears as a flickering flame to the naked eye. For that reason, she's often mistaken for a will-o'-the-wisp, which really gets her down. According to her, she just likes to keep moving and work up an appetite.","attack":"8200","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Fleet","imagePath":"Fleet.jpg","name":"Fleet","form":"Original Form","number":219,"rarity":"4","caption":"Where to next, captain?","defense":"9500","lore":"A Chinese warship that was in service around the end of the 2nd century. Ever since being chained up and set on fire during the Battle of Red Cliffs, she's awakened to her inner masochist. ","attack":"7500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Fleur Kitano","imagePath":"Fleur_Kitano.jpg","name":"Fleur Kitano","form":"Original Form","number":220,"rarity":"4","caption":"Let us dine among the fluttering petals...","defense":"6360","lore":"The soul of a plum tree that stands in Kyoto. She used to play tricks around Kyoto with her sister Fiorella, provoking the ire of the Ghost Guild.","attack":"7680","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Flick","imagePath":"Flick.jpg","name":"Flick","form":"Original Form","number":221,"rarity":"3","caption":"Oi! Wipe that smirk off yer face! No matter how I look, I'm actually real strong, y'know...","defense":"3050","lore":"The soul of a toy slingshot. He gets upset that nobody takes him seriously because he's only a toy, but his accuracy rate is very high. If he hits you, you'll definitely know about it...","attack":"6050","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Floe Angel","imagePath":"Floe_Angel.jpg","name":"Floe Angel","form":"Original Form","number":222,"rarity":"4","caption":"Cooey! I'm the biggest celebrity under the sea!","defense":"9500","lore":"The ghost of a sea slug that inhabits freezing oceans. As per her name, she likes nothing more than flapping her angelic wings. Despite calling herself a \"celebrity\", she doesn't do anything to warrant the label. (Unless showing off her \"assets\" around the harbor counts, that is...)\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Folding Fan","imagePath":"Folding_Fan.jpg","name":"Folding Fan","form":"Original Form","number":223,"rarity":"4","caption":"Watch me as I dance... It will be the image you take to the grave.","defense":"7800","lore":"Even someone who seems all sweetness and light at first can turn out to have a sharp tongue. But in the case of this spirited spirit, it's not just her tongue that's sharp... She conceals a deadly blade she keeps folded away that she can bare in a flash and use to cut her foes to ribbons. She may seem to be a mild-mannered shrine maiden, but she is in fact a highly-trained ninja warrior.","attack":"10400","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Folding Screen Lion","imagePath":"Folding_Screen_Lion.jpg","name":"Folding Screen Lion","form":"Original Form","number":224,"rarity":"3","caption":"Grroowwwllll! (Purr...)","defense":"7500","lore":"The Anima of a lion that leaped from a folding screen painted by a famous artist. (A still life for the 3D-crazed 21st century, perhaps?) She's pretty affectionate for the spirit of a lion, however, and enjoys being around people. Needless to say, she's a fearsome opponent in battle.","attack":"500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Forneus","imagePath":"Forneus.jpg","name":"Forneus","form":"Original Form","number":225,"rarity":"4","caption":"For you, I will destroy...everything...","defense":"8000","lore":"A devil that has taken the form of a sea-monster, she is listed as one of the 72 demons in the Key of Solomon. The Grand Marquis of the Underworld, she is said to command a total of 29 armies. She was released from her sealstone on the condition that she would lend her powers to Player alone.","attack":"8000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Fox Too","imagePath":"Fox_Too.jpg","name":"Fox Too","form":"Original Form","number":226,"rarity":"4","caption":"So you have a wish? Well, feel free to tell me more. I can't guarantee anything though...","defense":"9800","lore":"The guardian spirit of a historic shrine in Kyoto. He comes as a pair with Fox Wan. Compared to Fox Wan he is quite the playboy, and vain with it. He loves tofu sushi.","attack":"4500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Fox Wan","imagePath":"Fox_Wan.jpg","name":"Fox Wan","form":"Original Form","number":227,"rarity":"4","caption":"What is it you're after? Success in business?","defense":"9800","lore":"The guardian spirit of a historic shrine in Kyoto. He comes as a pair with Fox Too. He's less talkative than Fox Too, and tends to express himself using his eyes. He loves eating udon noodles.","attack":"4500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Francis Drake","imagePath":"Francis_Drake.jpg","name":"Francis Drake","form":"Original Form","number":228,"rarity":"4","caption":"Pop stars are the greatest treasures of all!","defense":"8300","lore":"This multi-talented ghost is both buccaneer and naval admiral...as well as being a hardcore pop fan. He travels the world scouting for the pop superstars of tomorrow. He insists on referring to this as \"treasure hunting\". While his interest in pop stars marks him out as a little eccentric, there's nothing strange about his skills at the helm of a ship, and he is trusted by all who ply their trade on the high seas. He prefers to conceal his passion for pop stars, for fear that he won't be taken seriously. He seems like a character with no shortage of secrets.","attack":"7900","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Frankie #1","imagePath":"Frankie_1.jpg","name":"Frankie #1","form":"","number":229,"rarity":"4","caption":"","defense":"5800","lore":"","attack":"7800","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Frankie #2","imagePath":"Frankie_2.jpg","name":"Frankie #2","form":"","number":230,"rarity":"3","caption":"","defense":"3700","lore":"","attack":"3750","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Fridgella","imagePath":"Fridgella.jpg","name":"Fridgella","form":"Original Form","number":231,"rarity":"3","caption":"You got any drinks you need cooling?","defense":"6500","lore":"The Anima of a refrigerator that was all the rage among 1950's housewives. Known for her icy stare, it's notoriously difficult to make her laugh. On the other hand, her cool and aloof character has earned her many an adoring fan, especially among girls who want to be like her.","attack":"7100","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Fuguruma Faerie","imagePath":"Fuguruma_Faerie_Ultimate.jpg","name":"Fuguruma Faerie","form":"Original Form","number":232,"rarity":"4","caption":"Let me read you some of this book. I warn you though: it'll make you cry...","defense":"9200","lore":"The soul of a cart used for transporting books. Her idea of ultimate bliss is reading one of her favorite romance novels out loud to someone.","attack":"8500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Fuguruma Faerie","imagePath":"Fuguruma_Faerie.jpg","name":"Fuguruma Faerie","form":"Ultimate Form","number":233,"rarity":"3","caption":"I poured my heart out into these pages... You will read them all, won't you?","defense":"6300","lore":" The soul of a cart used for transporting books. Since Player has started reading her love stories every night, her feelings of adoration have grown so strong that she's taken to writing down and sending them.","attack":"5500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Fujiwara no Hidesato","imagePath":"Fujiwara_no_Hidesato.jpg","name":"Fujiwara no Hidesato","form":"Original Form","number":234,"rarity":"4","caption":"It is time for your spirit to be sealed away once more.","defense":"9800","lore":"The nobleman and military leader who originally suppressed Taira no Masakado's revolt. He tends to shun the center stage and prefers to exert influence from the shadows. Still, he always seems to be in the right place at the right time, and he makes his action count. His legacy lives on, in spite of his low profile. The very definition of a man who gets things done.","attack":"7050","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Fukurokuju","imagePath":"Fukurokuju.jpg","name":"Fukurokuju","form":"Original Form","number":235,"rarity":"4","caption":"Oh, I don't know if I'll be able to play properly if you're staring at me like that, Player...","defense":"9000","lore":"The goddess responsible for luck, rewards, and longevity, and one of the seven lucky deities. She is celestially active as the bass player of the band called Seventh Heaven. It is her job to keep all the members of the band in line.","attack":"9000","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Fuma Shuriken","imagePath":"Fuma_Shuriken.jpg","name":"Fuma Shuriken","form":"Original Form","number":236,"rarity":"3","caption":"Ready...steady... And throw!","defense":"6150","lore":"The soul of a Shuriken throwing star used by the Fuma Ninjas who served the Hojo warrior clan in Japan's Sengoku period. It's a lot heavier than it looks. The head of the Fuma Ninjas, Shotaro Fuma, used to throw it with one hand.","attack":"5550","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Furiae","imagePath":"Furiae.jpg","name":"Furiae","form":"Original Form","number":237,"rarity":"5","caption":"Blame not the sin, but the person who committed it!","defense":"11000","lore":"A goddess of revenge. Furiae is a deadly serious character, who refuses to let even the smallest of human vices slide in her quest to punish all evil. A vengeful daemon at heart, she eliminates anyone who has committed a misdeed, regardless of its nature. She believes that sins merely exist, and that it is the humans who commit them that are the real evil that must be purged. She has recently become worried that she'll eventually run out of people to punish, and has been trying to keep her cool by averting her eyes from sin whenever possible.","attack":"11800","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Furinkazan Motto","imagePath":"Furinkazan_Motto.jpg","name":"Furinkazan Motto","form":"Original Form","number":238,"rarity":"4","caption":"Like a mountain, I move for no man.","defense":"9500","lore":"The motto inscribed on the banner of Shingen Takeda. Since taking on ghostly form, this spirit has acted as the body double for its master on the battlefield. This means that even if Shingen were to suddenly, let's say, become a woman, he would still have an original manly version to hold the fort.","attack":"9500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Furoshiki Cloth","imagePath":"Furoshiki_Cloth.jpg","name":"Furoshiki Cloth","form":"Original Form","number":239,"rarity":"4","caption":"Yippee! It's bath time!","defense":"9500","lore":"Bath supplies are not the only things she has bundled up in that silk wrapper she's so proud of. They say there's actually a portal to another dimension in there where she stores countless useful items. Like, for example, a cannon that obliterates its targets with compressed air.","attack":"9500","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Futsu-No-Mitama","imagePath":"Futsu-No-Mitama.jpg","name":"Futsu-No-Mitama","form":"Original Form","number":240,"rarity":"5","caption":"I put myself entirely in your service. You have my complete trust, comrade.","defense":"5600","lore":"The soul of a divine blade that appears in Japanese Mythology. It was once used by god Takemikazuchi to keep peace over the Middle Country of Japanese Mythology. Seeking a strong master with whom to rule the land once more, it became Player daemon.","attack":"11800","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Galatea","imagePath":"Galatea.jpg","name":"Galatea","form":"Original Form","number":241,"rarity":"5","caption":"Your Anima all seem terribly happy, don't they?","defense":"9990","lore":"A great beauty in Greek mythology. She came into being as a statue created by Pygmalion, but was granted the gift of life by the goddess Aphrodite. She now lives with an agent.","attack":"9990","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Gan Jiang & Mo Ye","imagePath":"Gan_Jiang_%2526_Mo_Ye.jpg","name":"Gan Jiang & Mo Ye","form":"Original Form","number":242,"rarity":"5","caption":"YAAOORGGH! Fancy testing out the power of these legendary weapons?","defense":"7200","lore":"A pair of swords kept in a single scabbard, born in China. Gan Jiang boasts an elegant black honeycomb pattern, while Mo Ye has a faint shadowed effect. It is said that their Anima's protection has kept the two together all this time.","attack":"13300","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Gargoyle","imagePath":"Gargoyle.jpg","name":"Gargoyle","form":"Original Form","number":243,"rarity":"4","caption":"Garrg... Garrg... ( I'm getting pins and needles standing still like this )","defense":"9050","lore":"A statue demon which stands still on the edge of a rooftop, disposing of accumulated rainwater.The gargoyle is also an excellent gatekeeper. He has difficulty speaking, and his words come out as a series of growls. He takes care over his appearance, and is rather fond of his macho physique.","attack":"6950","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Gentleman Rocker Cyril","imagePath":"Gentleman_Rocker_Cyril.jpg","name":"Gentleman Rocker Cyril","form":"Original Form","number":244,"rarity":"3","caption":"Prepare to have your heart rocked, baby.","defense":"3500","lore":"A ghost with a particular penchant for rock 'n' roll dance. He has trained in, and mastered, all forms of dance. As for why he chose rock 'n' roll? Because it's the grooviest, baby. He draws on his extensive knowledge of all things rhythmical to work as a dance commentator, too. He's secretly trying to bring the word \"groovy\" back into common parlance. Whatever next? Gnarly? ","attack":"6200","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Geo Cindy","imagePath":"Geo_Cindy.jpg","name":"Geo Cindy","form":"Original Form","number":245,"rarity":"5","caption":"What do you MEAN the world doesn't revolve around me?!","defense":"14000","lore":"Anima of the Ptolemaic model of astronomy, in which it was thought that the world was at the orbital center of all celestial bodies. Convinced that only she holds the key to understanding the universe, she can be quite the handful if you engage her in debate. She's comes from a rich family, a fact which might go some way to explaining her sense of entitlement...","attack":"11800","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Geronimo","imagePath":"Geronimo.jpg","name":"Geronimo","form":"Original Form","number":246,"rarity":"4","caption":" Fight to the last man! Don't yeild!","defense":"9500","lore":"The Anima of a tribe of Native Americans who fought to the last to defend their land from invaders. Their frenzied fighting style is said to spring from the vengeance they feel on behalf of their fallen comrades. any invaders who witnessed their wrath soon turned and fled the other way.","attack":"9500","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Giant Oarfish","imagePath":"Giant_Oarfish.jpg","name":"Giant Oarfish","form":"Original Form","number":247,"rarity":"4","caption":"I will be your guide through the darkness of the watery depths. Now come, follow me.","defense":"9160","lore":"The incarnation of a deep sea fish who serves as a guide at the Palace of the Dragon King. By lighting up its body, it also functions as a formidable bodyguard against some of the fiercer inhabitants of the ocean depths.","attack":"9000","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Giara","imagePath":"Giara.jpg","name":"Giara","form":"Original Form","number":248,"rarity":"5","caption":"Huh? Where am I? I don't think I can walk any further...","defense":"10000","lore":"A hardcore online gamer who got sucked into cyberspace. Her battle name is Giara and she's a warrior belonging to the 'Grilled Meat Gobblers' Guild.","attack":"10000","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Gift Box","imagePath":"Gift_Box.jpg","name":"Gift Box","form":"Original Form","number":249,"rarity":"4","caption":"Take whichever one you like.","defense":"8200","lore":"A spirit that was formed from the mountains of presents under Christmas trees around the world. She symbolizes the hopes and dreams of every child. Although she embodies so many things, she takes the form of an individual female ghost. She appears to them in the form that each child desires.","attack":"6650","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Glacie","imagePath":"Glacie.jpg","name":"Glacie","form":"Original Form","number":250,"rarity":"4","caption":"I'll make you a personalize cocktail. I call it...Piercing Love!","defense":"7050","lore":"The soul of an ice pick. He's always more than willing to break up some ice and make you a nice cool drink. Get in his way, though, and you might find yourself at the mercy of his sharper end...","attack":"9100","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Glasya-Labolas","imagePath":"Glasya-Labolas.jpg","name":"Glasya-Labolas","form":"Original Form","number":251,"rarity":"4","caption":"Do you wish to be torn to shreds?","defense":"9200","lore":"A spirit known as the patron saint of slaughter, she haunts the shadows of respectable society. Fall into her clutches and she will present you with two choices: die now, or die later. Basically, she's not a very nice person.","attack":"7200","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Gluttonous Crockery","imagePath":"Gluttonous_Crockery.jpg","name":"Gluttonous Crockery","form":"Original Form","number":252,"rarity":"4","caption":"Keep eating! I know you've got room for more!","defense":"6200","lore":"An embodiment of pure greed who appears in the autumn. Autumn is the time to loosen your belt and chow down as everyone starts fattening themselves up for winter. Ghosts are no exception, and otherworldly restaurants are full to bursting. This gluttonous ghost will keep serving you food until you're ready to burst. The courses just keep coming. ","attack":"8300","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Gnome","imagePath":"Gnome.jpg","name":"Gnome","form":"Original Form","number":253,"rarity":"3","caption":"I sure hope Rose Whip doesn't end up lashing me again...","defense":"4200","lore":"A spirit of the earth and one of the Four Elements. What with Titania stealing her candy and the Sylph sisters' light teasing, the forest spirits like to play around with her a bit, but she doesn't mind all that much. ","attack":"3600","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Go-Go","imagePath":"Go-Go.jpg","name":"Go-Go","form":"Original Form","number":254,"rarity":"4","caption":"How will you respond to my next move?","defense":"6300","lore":"A spirit that visits dedicated players of Go, a traditional Chinese board game. Playing with him will lead to a marked improvement in your game. He has been really looking forward to teaching you the rules.","attack":"6300","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Goddess of Good Fortune","imagePath":"Goddess_of_Good_Fortune.jpg","name":"Goddess of Good Fortune","form":"Original Form","number":255,"rarity":"5","caption":"Forget about fortune tellers. If I'm around, happiness is guaranteed!","defense":"15000","lore":"A goddess who brings good luck to all around her. She is especially fond of money, drinking, and fine clothes, and is usually found hanging around seedy areas where money changes hands, talking about love. She is the nemesis of the Goddess of Poverty.","attack":"11000","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Goddess of Misfortune","imagePath":"Goddess_of_Misfortune.jpg","name":"Goddess of Misfortune","form":"Original Form","number":256,"rarity":"2","caption":"Hey! Why the long face? I'm coming to GET YOU...!","defense":"2790","lore":"It's said that all who come into contact with this goddess will be struck by disaster. She's still a goddess though, so perhaps treating her well might pay off...?","attack":"3930","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Goddess of Misfortune","imagePath":"Goddess_of_Misfortune_Ultimate.jpg","name":"Goddess of Misfortune","form":"Ultimate Form","number":257,"rarity":"3","caption":"Heeey! I think it's time for some fun, don't you!?","defense":"5218","lore":"It's said that all who come into contact with this goddess will be struck by disaster. However, you treated her well, so she now summons good fortune!","attack":"6470","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Goddess of Misfortune","imagePath":"Goddess_of_Misfortune_HW.jpg","name":"Goddess of Misfortune [HW]","form":"Halloween Form","number":258,"rarity":"4","caption":"This outfit suits me, wouldn't you say? I'd be happy to dress like this for a while.","defense":"6300","lore":"It's said that all who come into contact with this goddess will be struck by disaster. She has come all the way to the Halloween Tower to meet you.","attack":"7650","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Goddess of Poverty","imagePath":"Goddess_of_Poverty.jpg","name":"Goddess of Poverty","form":"Original Form","number":259,"rarity":"2","caption":"Umm... Sorry to be a nuisance, but... Pleased to meet you!","defense":"3430","lore":"It's said that all who come into contact with this goddess will be struck bankrupt. She's still a goddess though, so perhaps treating her well might pay off...?","attack":"2810","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Goddess of Poverty","imagePath":"Goddess_of_Poverty_Ultimate.jpg","name":"Goddess of Poverty","form":"Ultimate Form","number":260,"rarity":"3","caption":"Hello there! Wait, come back! I've turned over a new leaf!","defense":"5970","lore":"It's said that all who come into contact with this goddess will be plagued by poverty. However, you treated her well, so she now summons good fortune!","attack":"5030","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Goddess of Poverty","imagePath":"Goddess_of_Poverty_HW.jpg","name":"Goddess of Poverty [HW]","form":"Halloween Form","number":261,"rarity":"4","caption":"Tee hee hee! It's so nice to be here with you!","defense":"8450","lore":"It is said that all who come into contact with this goddess will be plagued by poverty. She has come all the way to the Halloween Tower to meet you.","attack":"7560","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Goemon Ishikawa","imagePath":"Goemon_Ishikawa.jpg","name":"Goemon Ishikawa","form":"Original Form","number":262,"rarity":"5","caption":"There's nothing that I can't steal! I'll steal your hearts too, just you wait!","defense":"12000","lore":"An Iga ninja and a follower of Tanba Momochi, Goemon used to operate alongside an owl. During the ninja period, he was a cold-hearted character, who never spared a thought for his fellow man. As soon as the Warring States period changed into the Edo period, however, he realized that the days of the ninja were numbered, and transformed himself into a master thief. His ninja past gave him an insight into the immoral acts perpetrated by statesmen and other leaders, and this is perhaps the reason he became an honourable thief -- in order to exact a measure of indirect revenge.","attack":"13800","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Golden Angel","imagePath":"Golden_Angel.jpg","name":"Golden Angel","form":"Original Form","number":263,"rarity":"3","caption":"It looks like you've got something to say... Go on then! I can't wait to listen to you squeal!","defense":"6500","lore":"An angel who is very proud of her beautiful singing voice. She excels at making nasty comments that rub people up the wrong way. Some people enjoy such treatment, while others are not so keen.","attack":"4000","type":"Divina"},{"rawname":"Great Galactic Bridge","imagePath":"Great_Galactic_Bridge.jpg","name":"Great Galactic Bridge","form":"Original Form","number":264,"rarity":"4","caption":"Ah, there's never been a greater time than right now!","defense":"7580","lore":"The anima of a galaxy-spanning bridge. He has enjoyed a long acquaintance with Hikoboshi and Orihime, and thinks of them as family. Still, they've never quite got round to sharing their cell phone numbers with him... Still, this ghost is grown-up, so he doesn't get too worried about minor social slights.","attack":"9150","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Great Poet Kanesada","imagePath":"Great_Poet_Kanesada.jpg","name":"Great Poet Kanesada","form":"Original Form","number":265,"rarity":"5","caption":"Are you the 37th...?","defense":"13000","lore":"Given the name \"Great Poet\" after Tadaoki Hosokawa had executed the 36 vassals. The Anima of a Japanese sword that holds great destructive power.","attack":"16200","type":"Anima"},{"rawname":"Greedy Merchant","imagePath":"Greedy_Merchant.jpg","name":"Greedy Merchant","form":"Original Form","number":266,"rarity":"3","caption":"Ka-CHING! Money is the only thing I need!","defense":"5000","lore":"An embodiment of avarice who appears in late autumn. There is only one thing on her mind...money. She would say goodbye to her boyfriend for a pile of cold, hard cash. She would sell her own family for funds. She'd swap her friends for a fistful of dollars. Peace? Love? Harmony? Not if it doesn't pay... She'd sacrifice her own life for a paycheck. So long as you've got money, everything's going to be fine! With this philosophy of life, what could possibly go wrong?","attack":"5500","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Gregory","imagePath":"Gregory.jpg","name":"Gregory","form":"Original Form","number":267,"rarity":"4","caption":"I solved it! This is totally gonna change the world!","defense":"6500","lore":"Phantom of the Gregorian calendar, which was introduced in 1582 to replace the Julian version. He can be found at his desk every day, engrossed in his studies from morning to night. He's never happier than the moment he finally solves a mathematical problem that's been stumping him for ages. Unfortunately for him, however, the problems are so advanced that he's unable to share his elation with anybody else!","attack":"8300","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Gremlin","imagePath":"Gremlin.jpg","name":"Gremlin","form":"Original Form","number":268,"rarity":"3","caption":"It's hardly my fault that you lost all your data, is it? I've told you before to back up properly...","defense":"5900","lore":"A fairy who wreaks havoc on machines. To her favorite people only, she'll offer technical support and an excellent repair service for free.","attack":"6450","type":"Phantom"},{"rawname":"Gretel","imagePath":"Gretel_Anima.jpg","name":"Gretel","form":"","number":269,"rarity":"4","caption":"","defense":"5740","lore":"","attack":"8300","type":"Anima"}];